%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bajrang%20Dal%20Leader%20Bittu%20Bajrangi%20Arrested%20in%20Nuh%20Violence%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16102201%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-10.21.32-AM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3ESelf-proclaimed%20%E2%80%98cow%20vigilante%E2%80%99%20and%20Bajrang%20Dal%20member%20Bittu%20Bajrangi%2C%20who%20is%20based%20out%20of%20Faridabad%2C%20has%20been%20arrested%20by%20the%20police%20on%20Tuesday%20(August%2015)%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20communal%20violence%20in%20Nuh%2C%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViolence%20broke%20out%20in%20Nuh%20and%20spread%20over%20the%20district%20on%20July%2031%2C%20when%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal%20and%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20took%20out%20a%20%E2%80%98Shobha%20Yatra%E2%80%99%20through%20Muslim-majority%20areas%20carrying%20weapons%20and%20allegedly%20used%20provocative%20slogans.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fbittu-bajranji-runs-as-plainclothed-cops-chase-with-sticks-in-dramatic-video-before-arrest-101692144063870.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Bittu%20Bajrangi%20was%20present%20at%20the%20rally%20and%20allegedly%20snatched%20weapons%20from%20policement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fnuh-violence-bajrang-dal-member-bittu-bajrangi-arrested-from-faridabad-8894069%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20video%20of%20the%20arrest%20shows%20Bittu%20Bajrangi%20attempting%20to%20flee%20while%20around%2020%20policemen%20in%20plain%20clothes%20chase%20and%20eventually%20capture%20him%20in%20Faridabad%E2%80%99s%20Dabua.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBittu%20Bajrangi%E2%80%99s%20real%20name%20is%20Raj%20Kumar.%20He%20is%20the%20Faridabad%20chief%20of%20the%20Gau%20Raksha%20Bajrang%20Force.%20In%2