fficial%20vehicle%20and%20began%20shouting%20slogans%20against%20the%20police%E2%80%A6%20(They)%20broke%20the%20rear%20window%E2%80%A6%20took%20away%20the%20seized%20weapons%20and%20threatened%20police%20officers.%20They%20acted%20against%20the%20law%20by%20using%20illegal%20weapons%20and%20threatening%20behaviour%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20complaint%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%2015-20%20people%20have%20been%20named%20in%20the%20FIR%20and%20charged%20under%20various%20sections%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBajrangi%20had%20been%20arrested%20earlier%20this%20month%20for%20a%20provocative%20video%20posted%20on%20social%20media%20on%20July%2031%20morning%2C%20but%20was%20then%20released%20on%20bail.%20He%20has%20previously%20also%20featured%20in%20multiple%20hate%20speech-related%20FIRs.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692161604000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16102201%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-10.21.32-AM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fbajrang-dal-leader-bittu-bajrangi-arrested-in-nuh-violence-case%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20police%20officer's%20complaint%20accused%20Bajrangi%20of%20snatching%20weapons%20from%20the%20police%20during%20the%20'Shobha%20Yatra'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fbajrang-dal-leader-bittu-bajrangi-arrested-in-nuh-violence-case%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20WFH%20employee%20in%20Australia%20is%20hitting%20out%20at%20her%20ex-employer%20after%20it%20tracked%20how%20much%20she%20was%20typing%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20fired%20her%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226583%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hands%20typing%20on%20a%20laptop%20keyboard.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64dc46534ef9f30019f7ba79%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3