%20accountability%20for%20these%20crimes%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20work%20vigilantly%20with%20our%20law%20enforcement%20partners%20to%20protect%20all%20of%20our%20communities%20from%20hateful%2C%20ideologically%20driven%20acts%20of%20violence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FPolitics%2Fphiladelphia-teen-arrested-charged-fbi-terrorism-investigation%2Fstory%3Fid%3D102263409%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EABC%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20teen%20allegedly%20had%20acquired%20chemicals%20and%20had%20taken%20steps%20to%20build%20a%20weapon%20of%20mass%20destruction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmong%20the%20items%20he%20purchased%20were%20tactical%20equipment%2C%20wiring%2C%20chemicals%20and%20devices%20often%20used%20as%20remote%20detonators%2C%26quot%3B%20FBI%20Special%20Agent%20in%20Charge%20Jacqueline%20Maguire%20said%20at%20the%20news%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20had%20not%20only%20taken%20steps%20in%20acquiring%20those%20items%20and%20materials%20that%20are%20commonly%20used%20in%20improvised%20explosive%20devices%2C%20but%20he%20had%20also%20taken%20steps%20to%20start%20putting%20potential%20devices%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Maguire%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20started%20when%20the%20FBI%20became%20aware%20of%20the%20teen's%20alleged%20communication%20with%20Katibat%20al%20Tawhid%20wal%20Jihad%20(KTJ)%2C%20a%20foreign%20terrorist%20organization%20affiliated%20with%20al%20Qaeda.%20Over%20a%20period%20of%20weeks%2C%20the%20FBI%20identified%20the%20teen%20and%20conducted%20an%20investigation%2C%20which%20included%20surveillance%2C%20the%20media%20outlet%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Maguire%20also%20revealed%20that%20the%20teen%20also%20had%20access%20to%20quite%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20firearms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teen%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20weapons%20of%20mass%20destruction%2C%20criminal%20conspiracy%2C%20arson%2C%20causing%20or%20risking%20catastrophe%2C%20attempt%20to%20commit%20criminal%20mischief%2C%20possession%20of%20an%20instrument%20of%20crime%2C%20and%20reckless%20endangerment%20of%20another%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20was%20filed%20in%20juvenile%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692153660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-05%2F4tqmje88_fbi-reuters_625x300_30_May_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-teen-with-al-qaeda-links-arrested-for-plotting-terror-attack-fbi-4301318%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20investigation%20started%20when%20the%20FBI%20became%20aware%20of%20the%20teen's%20alleged%20communication%20with%20Katibat%20al%20Tawhid%20wal%20Jihad%20(KTJ).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-teen-with-al-qaeda-links-arrested-for-plotting-terror-attack-fbi-4301318%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-teen-with-al-qaeda-links-arrested-for-plotting-terror-attack-fbi-4301318%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-teen-with-al-qaeda-links-arrested-for-plotting-terror-attack-fbi-4301318%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Akshay%20Kumar%20Terminated%20Lucrative%20Contract%20To%20Save%20Delhi%20IPL%20Franchise%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHe%20could%20have%20easily%20played%20hardball%20with%20all%20the%20aces%20up%20his%20sleeve%20but%20Bollywood%20star%20Akshay%20Kumar%20instead%20terminated%20his%20lucrative%20contract%20with%20Delhi%20Daredevils%20(now%20Capitals)%20in%202009%20after%20the%20IPL%20franchise%20needed%20to%20cut%20down%20on%20losses%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20book.%20The%20incident%20has%20been%20mentioned%20in%20detail%20in%20veteran%20cricket%20administrator%20Amrit%20Mathur's%20autobiography%20'Pitchside%3A%20My%20Life%20in%20Indian%20Cricket'%20published%20by%20Westland%20Sport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAkshay%20signed%20a%20three-year%20deal%20with%20Delhi%20Daredevils%20to%20shoot%20promotional%20films%2C%20attend%20meet%20and%20greet%20events%20and%20make%20appearances%20at%20corporate%20events...%26quot%3B%20Mathur%20wrote%20in%20his%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BApart%20from%20Kotla%20act%20(he%20performed%20daring%20stunts)%2C%20nothing%20much%20happened%20because%20DD%20didn't%20know%20how%20to%20leverage%20him.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20season%2C%20during%20elaborate%20post-mortem%20held%20against%20backdrop%20of%20serious%20financial%20losses%2C%20DD%20decided%20to%20cancel%20or%20renegotiate%20the%20contract.%26quot%3B%20Mathur%20went%20on%20to%20write%20how%20it%20became%20an%20arduous%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAkshay's%20contract%20provided%20no%20exit%3B%20on%20the%20contrary%2C%20it%20gave%20him%20solid%20guarantees%20for%20a%20period%20of%20three%20years.%20DD's%20lawyers%20approached%20Akshay's%20staff%2C%20wanting%20to%20revisit%20the%20contract%2C%20but%20they%20made%20no%20headway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20(legally%20correct)%20response%20from%20his%20side%20was%20that%20contract%20didn't%20factor%20in%20early%20termination%20and%20it%20has%20run%20its%20course%20with%20full%20monetary%20compensation%2C%26quot%3B%20Mathur%20recalled%20in%20his%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSeen%20from%20perspective%20of%20DD%2C%20Akshay's%20multi-crore%20contract%20could%20be%20equated%20to%20a%20self%20goal%20or%20hit-wicket%20dismissal.%20Considering%20the%20disastrous%20financial%20results%20and%20need%20for%20austerity%2C%20the%20star%20had%20become%20an%20avoidable%20expense.%20Knowing%20there%20was%20no%20legal%20lifeline%20available%2C%20DD%20appealed%20to%20Akshay%20for%20mercy.%26quot%3B%20Mathur%20claimed%20in%20his%20book%20that%20he%20was%20the%20designated%20trouble-shooter%20for%20DD%20and%20met%20the%20star%20in%20his%20vanity%20van%20during%20the%20shooting%20of%20Chandni%20Chowk%20to%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20shot%2C%20we%20returned%20to%20his%20vanity%20van%20and%20I%2C%20very%20hesitantly%2C%20explained%20the%20reason%20for%20my%20visit%20and%20outlined%20DD's%20financial%20troubles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20problem%20ji%2C%20he%20said%20in%20a%20sympathetic%20manner.%20If%20it's%20not%20working%2C%20let's%20close%20it.%20I%20thought%20I%20hadn't%20heard%20him%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSeeing%20my%20confused%20look%2C%20he%20clarified%20slowly%2C%20'Isko%20khatam%20kar%20dete%20hain%20(let%20us%20end%20this)'.%20When%20I%20mumbled%20about%20the%20stringent%20contract%20clauses%2C%20he%20reassured%20me%2C%20'Koi%20baat%20nahin%2C%20main%20lawyer%20ko%20bol%20dunga%20(No%20problem%2C%20I%20will%20tell%20the%20lawyer)'.%26quot%3B%20The%20actor's%20magnanimity%20left%20him%20pleasantly%20surprised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMathur%20goes%20on%20to%20write%2C%20%26quot%3BEven%20after%20so%20many%20years%20I%20am%20surprised%20that%20Akshay%20waived%20off%20such%20a%20large%20amount%20of%20money.%20Just%20like%20that%20--%20snap%20decision%20when%20he%20could%20have%20easily%20thrown%20the%20contract%20at%20us.%26quot%3B%20The%20book%20takes%20a%20sneak%20peek%20into%20Indian%20cricket%20and%20Mathur's%20association%20with%20the%20establishment%20for%20three%20and%20half%20decades%20helped%20the%20readers%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20first-hand%20anecdotes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20anyone%20is%20looking%20for%20controversies%2C%20this%20is%20not%20the%20right%20book.%20While%20he%20narrates%20some%20feel-good%20anecdotes%20during%20his%20time%20as%20administrative%20and%20media%20manager%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20those%20are%20already%20known%20to%20cricket%20nerds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20eminently%20readable%20book%2C%20some%20of%20the%20wrong%20facts%20are%20however%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20letdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20place%20he%20writes%20(on%20Page%2029)%20that%20Ravi%20Shastri%20retired%20from%20all%20forms%20of%20cricket%20after%20the%20South%20Africa%20tour%20of%201992-93.%20That's%20the%20first%20wrong%20fact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Shastri%20never%20played%20for%20India%20after%20that%20tour%20but%20he%20captained%20Mumbai%20for%20the%20entire%201993-94%20season%2C%20and%20they%20won%20the%20final%20in%20March%2C%201994%20beating%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20even%20bigger%20glaring%20error%20is%20there%20on%20Page%2032%20and%2033%20where%20he%20mentions%20the%20famous%20Mankading%20incident%20involving%20Kapil%20Dev%20and%20Peter%20Kirsten%2C%20and%20subsequently%2C%20Kepler%20Wessels%20hitting%20the%20Indian%20legend%20on%20shin%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20turning%20for%20the%20second%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMathur%20wrote%20that%20the%20incident%20happened%20during%20a%20Test%20match%20as%20at%20one%20place%20he%20refers%20that%20Kapil%20told%20the%20team%20during%20tea%20time%20but%20it%20actually%20took%20place%20during%20an%20ODI%20game%20prior%20to%20the%20Tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20one%20was%20on%20Page%20187%20where%20he%20describes%20Irfan%20Pathan%20as%20a%20Test%20debutant%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lahore%20Test%20of%20Pakistan%20series%20in%202004.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Pathan%20had%20made%20his%20Test%20debut%20in%20Adelaide%20in%20December%202003%2C%20during%20the%20team's%20previous%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692153300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Flbscnhv8_akshay-kumar-twitter_625x300_16_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fhow-akshay-kumar-terminated-lucrative-contract-to-save-delhi-ipl-franchise-book-reveals-4300971%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Akshay%20Kumar%20had%20signed%20a%20three-year%20deal%20with%20Delhi%20D