0that%20India%20star%20Virat%20Kohli%20is%20his%20favourite%20batter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20current%20era%2C%20it's%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%26quot%3B%20Chaha%20Cricket%20told%20Nadir%20Ali%20on%20the%20latter's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZhtuOEf7xcM%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshow%20on%20YouTube%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKohli%20is%20an%20extremely%20big%20player%20currently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20speed%20at%20which%20Kohli%20hits%20the%20balls%20in%20the%20gap%20stands%20apart%20from%20other%20players.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20praising%20the%20likes%20of%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Babar%20Azam%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F59905-mohammad-babar-azam-playerprofile%5C%22%3EBabar%20Azam%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Mohammed%20Rizwan%2C%20Chacha%20Cricket%20said%20that%20he%20wishes%20the%20players%20in%20Pakistan%20play%20better%20than%20Kohli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20work%20front%2C%20Kohli%20is%20back%20to%20his%20rigorous%20training%20schedule.%20The%20former%20India%20captain%20played%20the%20Test%20series%20against%20West%20Indies%20and%20in%20one%20of%20the%20ODIs.%20After%20that%20he%20was%20rested%20for%20the%20remaining%20two%20games.%20It%20is%20worth%20noting%20that%20Kohli%20along%20with%20some%20other%20senior%20players%20was%20not%20named%20in%20India's%20T20I%20squad%20against%20the%20Caribbean%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli%20will%20again%20be%20seen%20in%20action%20at%20the%20Asia%20Cup%202023%20which%20begins%20on%20August%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20are%20yet%20to%20announce%20their%20squad%20for%20the%20tournament%20but%20many%20players%20have%20started%20their%20preparation.%20The%20tournament%20will%20follow%20a%20hybrid%20model%2C%20with%20four%20matches%20to%20be%20hosted%20by%20Pakistan%20and%20all%20of%20India's%20matches%20and%20a%20total%20of%20nine%20fixtures%20taking%20place%20in%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%