0HIMARS%20rockets.%20For%20its%20part%2C%20Russia%20has%20been%20able%20to%20use%20electronic%20warfare%20to%20send%20Ukraine's%20GPS-guided%20JDAM%20glide%20bombs%20and%20HIMARS%20rockets%20off%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Russia%20R-330Zh%20Zhitel%20electronic%20warfare%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64a2e6639fab2b00184af038%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Russian%20R-330Zh%20Zhitel%20electronic-warfare%20jamming%20station%20during%20an%20exercise%20in%20July%202018.%3Cp%3EDenis%20Abramov%2FRussian%20Defense%20Ministry%20via%20Mil.ru%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20success%20has%20spurred%20some%20US%20Army%20commanders%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-attacks-on-russia-us-army-command-post-vulnerability-2023-7%5C%22%3Eto%20warn%20about%20the%20vulnerability%20of%20their%20own%20command%20posts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20have%20an%20electronic%20footprint%20that%20they%20worry%20Chinese%20forces%20will%20easily%20be%20able%20to%20find.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20the%20US%20focus%20has%20been%20elsewhere%20and%20rivals%20have%20been%20investing%20in%20electronic-warfare%20capabilities%2C%20the%20US%20military%20%26quot%3Bwould%20likely%20face%20challenges%20protecting%20itself%20from%20electromagnetic%20attack%26quot%3B%20by%20%26quot%3Bour%20most%20advanced%20adversaries%2C%26quot%3B%20Brown%20told%20lawmakers%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20armies%20%E2%80%94%20or%20at%20least%20the%20high-tech%20ones%20%E2%80%94%20are%20vulnerable%20to%20electronic%20warfare%2C%20but%20the%20US%20military%20is%20especially%20vulnerable%20because%20its%20way%20of%20war%20is%20so%20dependent%20on%20electronic%20communications.%20Operations%20by%20forces%20across%20land%2C%20sea%2C%20air%2C%20space%2C%20and%20cyber%20are%20supposed%20to%20be%20precisely%20coordinated%20via%20data%20netw