%20own%20celebration%20in%20Kuki-majority%20Churachandpur%2C%2065%20km%20from%20the%20state%20capital%20Imphal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20these%20celebrations%2C%20we%20have%20shown%20that%20we%20are%20separate%20from%20the%20Manipur%20government%20and%20that%20we%20can%20rule%20and%20govern%20ourselves.%20We%20want%20to%20show%20the%20rest%20of%20India%20we%20would%20like%20to%20be%20a%20separate%20entity%20under%20the%20Indian%20Union%2C%26quot%3B%20Chinkhenpau%20from%20the%20Zomi%20Council%20Steering%20Committee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisuals%20of%20the%20event%20show%20young%20people%20marching%20in%20military%20battledress%20holding%20'assault%20rifles'.%20They%20wore%20the%20shoulder%20or%20chest%20patch%20of%20the%20Zomi%20Revolutionary%20Army%20(ZRA)%2C%20a%20Kuki%20insurgent%20group%20with%20whom%20the%20Manipur%20government%20ended%20the%20suspension%20of%20operations%20(SoO)%20agreement%20in%20March%20this%20year%2C%20two%20months%20before%20violence%20broke%20out%20between%20the%20hill-majority%20Kukis%20and%20the%20valley-majority%20Meiteis%20over%20the%20Meiteis'%20demand%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22sjnk81qg%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fsjnk81qg_kuki-march_625x300_16_August_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuki%20civil%20society%20groups%2C%20however%2C%20claimed%20the%20men%20in%20battledress%20who%20participated%20in%20the%20march%20were%20%26quot%3Bvillage%20defence%20volunteers%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20guns%20were%20not%20real.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20optics%20of%20the%20Churachandpur%20event%20that%20indicated%20the%20participation%20of%20'armed'%20men%2C%20however%2C%20has%20sparked%20a%20massive%20controversy%20in%20Manipur%20amid%20a%20tensed%20environment%20after%20the%20ethnic%20clashes%20that%20lasted%20three%20months.%20Sporadic%20fights%20continue%20to%20be%20reported%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20marches%20in%20Churachandpur%20has%20been%20criticised%20on%20social%20media%20over%20alleged%20disrespect%20shown%20to%20the%20national%20flag.%20In%20one%20of%20the%20videos%20of%20the%20event%2C%20the%20national%20flag%20is%20seen%20installed%20at%20an%20angle%2C%20with%20the%20stick%20jutting%20out%20quite%20a%20bit%2C%20giving%20it%20the%20appearance%20of%20a%20flag%20flown%20in%20half-mast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20video%2C%20a%20guerilla%20uniformed%20man%20in%20a%20group%20of%20marchers%2C%20instead%20of%20holding%20the%20national%20flag%20upright%20as%20mandated%20by%20the%20Flag%20Code%20of%20India%2C%202002%2C%20is%20seen%20dipping%20it%20to%20the%20side%20when%20he%20approaches%20some%20people%20standing%20on%20a%20podium%2C%20which%20is%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20law%20that%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20flag%20shall%20not%20be%20dipped%20in%20salute%20to%20any%20person%20or%20thing%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22oaquf8m8%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Foaquf8m8_kuki-march_625x300_16_August_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20has%20the%20unified%20command%20done%20about%20this%20open%20display%20of%20deadly%20weapons%20-%20toy%20gun%20as%20Kuki%20claims%3F%20If%20others%20too%20form%20such%20militia%2C%20will%20they%20be%20also%20allowed%20to%20display%20their%20illegal%20might%20in%20national%20parades%3F%20Will%20we%20allow%20'Ranbir%20Sena'%20or%20'Bhim%20Army'%20etc%20to%20do%20similar%20act%3F%26quot%3B%20Lieutenant%20General%20L%20Nishikanta%20Singh%20(retired)%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20Only%20security%20forces%20display%20weapons%20on%20parade.%20Kukis%20sending%20a%20message%20-%20can%20get%20away%20with%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lt%20General%20Singh%2C%20who%20also%20headed%20the%20Intelligence%20Corps%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%20before%20retiring%20in%202018%2C%20after%2040%20years%20of%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWhat%20has%20the%20unified%20command%20done%20about%20this%20open%20display%20of%20deadly%20weapons%20-%20toy%20gun%20as%20Kuki%20claims%3F%20If%20others%20too%20form%20such%20militia%2C%20will%20they%20be%20also%20allowed%20to%20display%20their%20illegal%20might%20in%20national%20parades%3F%20Will%20we%20allow%20'Ranbir%20Sena'%20or%20'Bhim%20Army'%20etc%20to%20do%20similar%20act.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fkg7P952IET%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fkg7P952IET%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Lt%20Gen%20L%20Nishikanta%20Singh%20(R)%20(%40VeteranLNSingh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FVeteranLNSingh%2Fstatus%2F1691453986052968448%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2015%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kuki%20civil%20society%20groups%20have%20claimed%20they%20are%20not%20secessionist%2C%20though%20they%20have%20been%20demanding%20a%20separate%20administration.%20They%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Independence%20Day%20celebrations%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20the%20Manipur%20government%2C%20sources%20said.%20The%20Kukis%20have%20some%2025%20insurgent%20groups%20that%20have%20signed%20the%20suspension%20of%20operations%20(SoO)%20agreement%20with%20the%20centre%2C%20military%20and%20the%20state%20government.%20The%20SoO%20insurgents%20live%20in%20designated%20camps%20and%20claim%20they%20have%20kept%20their%20weapons%20under%20lock%2C%20being%20monitored%20by%20the%20authorities%20regularly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kukis%20also%20screened%20the%20Vicky%20Kaushal-starrer%20'Uri%3A%20The%20Surgical%20Strike'%20in%20Churachandpur%2C%20billed%20as%20the%20first%20public%20screening%20of%20a%20Hindi%20movie%20in%20Manipur%20since%202000%2C%20when%20a%20valley-based%20insurgent%20group%20banned%20Bollywood%20films%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20many%20pointed%20out%20Hindi%20movies%20have%20been%20screened%20in%20Manipur%20in%20relative%20safety%2C%20the%20most%20recent%20being%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan-starrer%20'Pathaan'%20at%20a%20theatre%20in%20March%20this%20year%20in%20Ukhrul%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hmar%20Students%20Association%20said%20it%20screened%20the%20film%20to%20express%20its%20opposition%20to%20the%20ban%20on%20Hindi%20movies%20imposed%20by%20the%20Revolutionary%20People's%20Front%2C%20the%20political%20wing%20of%20the%20valley-based%20insurgent%20group%20People's%20Liberation%20Army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20over%20two%20decades%20since%20a%20movie%20was%20screened%20in%20our%20town.%20The%20Meiteis%20have%20banned%20Hindi%20movies%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20Today's%20move%20is%20to%20defy%20the%20anti-national%20policies%20of%20the%20Meitei%20groups%20and%20to%20show%20our%20love%20for%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Ginza%20Vualzong%2C%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20Kuki%20civil%20society%20group%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders'%20Forum%20(ITLF)%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%225hkoj4o%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F5hkoj4o_uri-screening_625x300_16_August_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVicky%20Kaushal-starrer%20'Uri%3A%20The%20Surgical%20Strike'%20was%20screened%20in%20Manipur's%20Churachandpur%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChampion%20boxer%20from%20Manipur%20Mary%20Kom's%20own%20biopic%20was%20also%20not%20released%20in%20her%20home%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeiteis%20on%20social%20media%2C%20however%2C%20condemned%20the%20coining%20of%20their%20entire%20community%20with%20valley-based%20legacy%20insurgent%20groups%20whose%20support%20base%20no%20longer%20exists.%20They%20pointed%20out%20that%20though%20no%20public%20screening%20of%20Bollywood%20movies%20has%20been%20held%20due%20to%20fear%20of%20the%20insurgents'%20diktat%2C%20they%20said%20Hi