k%20OK.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EYou%20can%20use%20the%20free%20utility%20called%20Fraps%20to%20measure%20your%20frame%20rate%20in%20any%20game.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20monitors%20have%20a%20built-in%20FPS%20counter%20that%20can%20be%20displayed%20on%20screen%20independent%20of%20your%20PC.%20You%20can%20look%20in%20your%20monitor's%20menu%20and%20settings%20to%20see%20if%20this%20feature%20is%20available.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20you%20know%20your%20PC's%20frame%20rate%20(and%20how%20it%20compares%20to%20your%20monitor's%20refresh%20rate)%2C%20you%20can%20try%20any%20of%20these%20tricks%20to%20increase%20your%20computer's%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Enable%20Game%20Mode%20in%20Windows%5C%22%3EEnable%20Game%20Mode%20in%20Windows%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EGame%20Mode%20configures%20a%20number%20of%20Windows%20settings%20with%20a%20single%20click%20to%20optimize%20your%20PC%20for%20gaming%20and%20maximize%20the%20display's%20frame%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3EClick%20the%20Search%20button%20and%20then%20click%20Settings.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20the%20Settings%20window's%20search%20box%20type%20game%20and%20then%20choose%20Game%20Mode%20settings%20in%20the%20search%20results.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIf%20it's%20not%20already%20turned%20on%2C%20enable%20Game%20Mode%20by%20swiping%20the%20button%20to%20the%20right.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQuick%20tip%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3EYou%20might%20need%20to%20restart%20your%20PC%20for%20the%20settings%20to%20take%20effect.%20Windows%2011%20has%20a%20Gaming%20tab%20within%20the%20Settings%20menu%20that%20offers%20the%20same%20Game%20Mode%20menu%20as%20Windows%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Screenshot%20of%20the%20Game%20Mode%20window.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62f172b38677d80018ee6768%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22525%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETurn%20on%20Windows%2010%20Game%20Mode%20to%20optimize%20your%20PC.%3Cp%3EDave%20Johnson%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Make%20sure%20you%20have%20the%20latest%20video%20driver%20installed%5C%22%3EMake%20sure%20you%20have%20the%20latest%20video%20driver%20installed%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMaking%20sure%20your%20computer's%20system%20updates%20and%20device%20drivers%20are%20up%20to%20date%20is%20essential%20to%20getting%20the%20best%20performance%20from%20your%20PC.%20There%20are%20two%20things%20you%20can%20do%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fhow-to-check-for-updates-on-windows-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECheck%20for%20Windows%20updates%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Click%20the%20Start%20button%20and%20choose%20%3Cstrong%3ESettings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20then%20type%20%3Cstrong%3EUpdates%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20and%20choose%20%3Cstrong%3ECheck%20for%20updates%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20in%20the%20search%20results.%20Use%20the%20Windows%20Update%20window%20to%20make%20sure%20you%20have%20the%20latest%20updates%20installed.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EUpdate%20the%20video%20card%20drivers.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20This%20happens%20automatically%20when%20you%20check%20for%20Windows%20updates%2C%20but%20there%20might%20be%20newer%20updates%20waiting%20for%20your%20graphics%20card%20as%20well.%20If%20you%20use%20Nvidia%20GeForce%20Experience%2C%20start%20the%20app%20and%20click%20%3Cstrong%3EDrivers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20window.%20Click%20%3Cstrong%3ECheck%20for%20updates%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20to%20see%20if%20there%20are%20any%20new%20ones%20to%20install.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221790%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Screenshot%20of%20GeForce%20driver%20update%20screen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62f172eacc15bf00182f7b0f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221343%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMake%20sure%20Windows%20is%20up%20to%20date%20and%20check%20for%20new%20video%20drivers%20as%20well.%3Cp%3EDave%20Johnson%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Optimize%20your%20game%20settings%5C%22%3EOptimize%20your%20game%20settings%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20game%20is%20different%2C%20but%20if%20your%20frame%20rate%20is%20too%20low%2C%20you%20can%20enter%20your%20game's%20settings%20screen%20and%20dial%20down%20the%20image%20quality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20might%20be%20a%20single%20switch%20you%20can%20throw%20to%20change%20the%20image%20quality%20from%20%26quot%3Bhigh%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3Bmedium%2C%26quot%3B%20for%20example%2C%20or%20you%20might%20need%20to%20set%20individual%20settings%20for%20viewing%20distance%2C%20shadows%2C%20texture%20effects%2C%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20games%20will%20let%20you%20set%20a%20target%20frame%20rate%2C%20and%20the%20game%20will%20then%20use%20dynamic%20resolution%20scaling%20to%20find%20a%20quality%20that%20matches%20your%20desired%20FPS.%20This%20is%20an%20AI-powered%20feature%20that%20requires%20a%20dedicated%20graphics%20card%2C%20but%20newer%20gaming%20PCs%20should%20be%20capable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Screenshot%20of%20a%20game%E2%80%99s%20graphics%20settings%20menu.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62f1733d8677d80018ee678d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22525%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EReduce%20the%20intensity%20of%20graphics%20in%20your%20games%20to%20get%20a%20significant%20performance%20boost.%3Cp%3EDave%20Johnson%2FInsiderDave%20Johnson%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Reduce%20your%20screen%20resolution%5C%22%3EReduce%20your%20screen%20resolution%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOften%20a%20separate%20setting%20in%20the%20game%20from%20video%20quality%2C%20try%20reducing%20the%20screen%20resolution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGo%20to%20your%20PC's%20Settings%2C%20select%20%3Cstrong%3ESystem%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20then%20%3Cstrong%3EAdvanced%20display%20settings%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20and%20choose%20a%20lower-resolution%20option%20from%20the%20Resolution%20menu.%20Many%20games%20will%20also%20let%20you%20select%20a%20specific%20resolution%20in%20the%20graphics%20menu%20that%20will%20only%20apply%20while%20the%20game%20is%20running.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20can%20have%20a%20dramatic%20effect%20on%20the%20frame%20rate%2C%20but%20can%20lead%20to%20graphics%20that%20look%20less%20detailed%20and%20sharp.%20Lower%20resolution%20also%20limits%20the%20amount%20of%20space%20available%20on%20screen%20when%20you're%20not%20gaming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Upgrade%20your%20graphics%20card%5C%22%3EUpgrade%20your%20graphics%20card%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20can't%20significantly%20improve%20your%20frame%20rate%20with%20these%20tips%2C%20you%20might%20have%20no%20other%20choice%3A%20upgrade%20your%20graphics%20card.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20might%20not%20be%20an%20option%20if%20you%20are%20gaming%20on%20a%20laptop%20(but%20there%20are%20exceptions%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20some%20Alienware%20laptops%2C%20for%20example%2C%20allow%20you%20to%20add%20an%20external%20%26quot%3BGraphics%20Amplifier%26quot%3B%20to%20upgrade%20your%20display%20quality).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20you%20have%20a%20desktop%20PC%2C%20you%20may%20be%20able%20to%20swap%20out%20your%20graphics%20card%20for%20one%20that%20dramatically%20enhances%20your%20frame%20rate%20and%20increases%20your%20performance.%20Alternatively%2C%20you%20could%20try%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-overclocking%5C%22%3Eoverclocking%20your%20PC%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20you%20have%20parts%20that%20allow%20it%2C%20but%20the%20benefits%20will%20vary%20depending%20on%20the%20game%20and%20other%20factors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C