es%20are%20marked%20up%20through%20Instacart.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20TikTok%20user%20said%20she%20paid%20%24513.77%20for%20%24435%20worth%20of%20groceries%2C%20plus%20fees%20and%20tip.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20time%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstacart-shoppers-say-they-cant-keep-working-after-pay-cut-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstacart%20shopper%3C%2Fa%3E%20fills%20an%20order%2C%20the%20Instacart%20app%20flashes%20a%20reminder%3A%20%26quot%3BDon't%20give%20the%20receipt%20to%20a%20customer%20or%20place%20it%20in%20a%20bag%20%E2%80%94%20they%20get%20a%20digital%20receipt%20from%20Instacart.%26quot%3B%20Shoppers%2C%20the%20term%20Instacart%20gives%20to%20the%20gig%20workers%20that%20fulfill%20orders%2C%20are%20then%20prompted%20to%20slide%20a%20button%20on-screen%20to%20acknowledge%20the%20requirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20sometimes%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstacart-kroger-customer-was-charged-278325-for-her-grocery-order-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstacart%20customers%3C%2Fa%3E%20get%20ahold%20of%20the%20receipt%20from%20the%20store%20anyway.%20And%20they%20can%20come%20to%20a%20startling%20realization%3A%20Items%20bought%20through%20Instacart%20are%20often%20more%20expensive%20than%20they%20would%20be%20in-store.%20The%20markups%20often%20surprise%20customers%2C%20three%20Instacart%20shoppers%20told%20Insider.%20Customers%20can%20be%20particularly%20annoyed%20because%20they%20also%20%3Cspan%3Epay%20various%20fees%20and%20often%20tip%20for%20delivery%20through%20Instacart.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shoppers%20who%20spoke%20with%20Insider%20requested%20anonymity%20for%20fear%20of%20retaliation%20from%20Instacart%2C%20including%20deactivation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22656%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20