stacart%20emails%20customers%20a%20receipt%20with%20a%20breakdown%20of%20Instacart's%20prices%20once%20the%20order%20is%20delivered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20some%20retailers%20on%20the%20Instacart%20platform%20choose%20to%20include%20item%20markups%2C%20our%20goal%20is%20to%20offer%20full%20transparency%20to%20customers%20as%20they%20shop%20on%20the%20platform%2C%26quot%3B%20Instacart%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstacart%20tells%20shoppers%20to%20keep%20the%20print%20receipt%20%26quot%3Bin%20case%20of%20any%20necessary%20returns%20or%20if%20they%20need%20to%20submit%20a%20receipt%20photo.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EInstacart%20customers%20don't%20always%20realize%20the%20markups%20exist%20unless%20they%20get%20a%20look%20at%20the%20receipt%20from%20the%20store%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20some%20customers%20get%20ahold%20of%20the%20store%20receipt%20anyway.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok%20user%20vane.ssota%20posted%20a%20video%20last%20month%20showing%20her%20paper%20receipt%20from%20an%20Instacart%20order%20from%20a%20Ralph's%20grocery%20store%20in%20California.%20She%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20on%20the%20video%20from%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20the%20TikToker%20compares%20the%20costs%20of%20items%20on%20her%20print%20receipt%20with%20those%20on%20the%20receipt%20that%20Instacart%20emailed%20her.%20Every%20item%20in%20the%20order%20was%20marked%20up%20by%20between%2050%20cents%20and%20%242%2C%20according%20to%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20cite%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40vane.ssota%2Fvideo%2F7257654751347789102%5C%22%20data-video-id%3D%5C%227257654751347789102%5C%22%3E%20%3Csection%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40vane.ssota%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20title%3D