C%20he%20would%20receive%20emails%20from%20fans%20mistaking%20him%20to%20be%20the%20actor.%20%26quot%3BI%20used%20to%20get%20letters%20from%20some%20of%20the%20actor's%20fans%20saying%20'I've%20always%20been%20in%20love%20with%20you%20and%20I%20didn't%20know%20you%20could%20do%20math%20and%20all%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Sal%20Khan%20said%20as%20Bill%20Gates%20laughed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWatch%20the%20video%20below%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F41_UxTASwKw%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESal%20Khan%20is%20the%20founder%20of%20Khan%20Academy%2C%20an%20American%20non-profit%20educational%20organisation%20that%20creates%20online%20tools%20to%20help%20educate%20students.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20conversation%20with%20Mr%20Gates%2C%20he%20also%20recounted%20an%20incident%20from%202015%20when%20he%20visited%20India%20and%20found%20himself%20live%20on%20television%20alongside%20Salman%20Khan%20due%20to%20their%20shared%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20clarified%20that%20despite%20the%20similarity%20in%20name%2C%20there%20is%20no%20Bollywood%20connection%20between%20them.%20But%20he%20playfully%20confessed%20his%20fondness%20for%20Bollywood%20movies%20and%20admitted%20that%20he%20watches%20them%20more%20than%20people%20might%20suspect%20and%20even%20makes%20his%20wife%20watch%20them%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnasa-confirms-july-2023-as-the-hottest-month-ever-says-we-must-act-now-4300074%5C%22%3ENASA%20Confirms%20July%202023%20As%20The%20Hottest%20Month%20Ever%2C%20Says%20''We%20Must%20Act%20Now''%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20the%20same%20podcast%2C%20Mr%20Gates%20also%20shared%20