%20cross%20between%20a%20detective%20thriller%20and%20a%20horror%20tragedy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20moving%20account%20of%20her%20childhood%20and%20an%20adult%20life%20spent%20seeking%20her%20biological%20parents%2C%20Ingrid%20von%20Oelhafen%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.co.in%2Fbooks%2Fedition%2FHitler_s_Forgotten_Children%2Fq2MXswEACAAJ%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHitler%E2%80%99s%20Forgotten%20Children%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20records%20how%20she%20was%20mystified%20by%20some%20family%20documents%20which%20listed%20her%20name%20as%20%E2%80%98Erika%20Matko%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPuzzled%2C%20von%20Oelhafen%20traverses%20archives%2C%20meets%20people%2C%20and%20pursues%20vague%20leads%20to%20trace%20the%20story%20of%20her%20birth.%20One%20puzzling%20document%20she%20unearths%20is%20a%20receipt%20that%20reads%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20family%20Hermann%20von%20Oelhafen%2C%20of%20Gentz%20Strasse%205%2C%20Munich%2C%20has%20on%203%20June%201944%2C%20taken%20into%20their%20home%20the%20ethnic%20German%20girl%20Erika%20Matkow%20%5Bsic%5D%2C%20born%2011%20November%201941.%20Because%20she%20is%20a%20child%20of%20German%20stock%2C%20on%20the%20orders%20of%20the%20Reichsfuhrer%20she%20is%20to%20be%20brought%20up%20in%20a%20German%20family.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20finally%20discovers%20accurate%20information%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CLilienthal%E2%80%99s%20research%20had%20found%20the%20name%20Erika%20Matko%20in%20some%20long-forgotten%20records%20%E2%80%A6%20She%20had%20been%20raised%20in%20one%20of%20its%20children%E2%80%99s%20homes%3A%20a%20place%20called%20Sonnenweise%20%E2%80%A6%20at%20Kohren-Sahlis.%20Since%20I%20was%20%E2%80%93%20or%20once%20had%20been%20%E2%80%93%20Erika%20Matko%2C%20that%20meant%20I%20was%20a%20Lebensborn%20baby%20%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EErika%20Matko%2FIngrid%20von%20Oelhafen%20was%20a%20%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E%20baby.%20The%20discovery%20inverts%20her%20sense%20of%20self%2C%20because%20she%20had%20lived%20under%20another%2C%20assumed%20identity%20all%20her%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20meaning%20%E2%80%98Fount%20or%20Fountain%20of%20Life%E2%80%99%2C%20was%20a%20Nazi%20organisation%20whose%20purpose%20was%20ostensibly%20to%20take%20care%20of%20expectant%20mothers%2C%20including%20unwed%20ones%2C%20who%20would%20produce%20healthy%20Aryan%20children%20to%20populate%20the%20Third%20Reich.%20Its%20principal%20officers%2C%20Gregor%20Ebner%2C%20Max%20Sollmann%20and%20others%20were%20prosecuted%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fencyclopedia.ushmm.org%2Fcontent%2Fen%2Farticle%2Fsubsequent-nuremberg-proceedings-case-8-the-rusha-case%5C%22%3ECase%208%20of%20the%20Subsequent%20Nuremberg%20Trials%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20but%20not%20executed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fhow-to-indict-persecutors%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20Indict%20Perpetrators%20%E2%80%93%20Nuremberg%E2%80%99s%20History%20Lessons%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20monitored%20directly%20by%20Heinrich%20Himmler%2C%20who%20even%20drew%20up%20dietary%20charts%20for%20expectant%20mothers.%20This%20organisation%2C%20the%20proverbial%20tip%20of%20the%20eugenics%20iceberg%2C%20had%20its%20origins%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98fear%20of%20small%20numbers%E2%80%99%2C%20to%20adapt%20Arjun%20Appadurai%E2%80%99s%20resonant%20phrase%3A%20the%20Nazi%20fear%20that%20the%20Aryan%20population%20was%20on%20the%20decline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fragmented%20%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E%20records%20are%20fascinating%20for%20what%20they%20reveal%20about%20theories%20of%20racial%20purity%2C%20the%20discourse%20of%20demographic%20decline%20and%20the%20exhortation%20to%20produce%20more%20numbers%20of%20a%20specific%20race%20in%20order%20to%20dominate%20the%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20%E2%80%98fear%20of%20small%20numbers%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20World%20War%20I%2C%20Germany%20had%20the%20sharpest%20birth-rate%20decline%20in%20Europe.%20In%201900%2C%20the%20statistics%20showed%20an%20average%20rate%20of%20births%20per%20thousand%20of%2035.8%2C%20but%20by%201932%2C%20it%20was%20down%20to%2014.7.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20German%20population%20of%2037%20million%20in%201885%20had%20produced%20the%20same%20number%20of%20children%20as%20the%20population%20of%2067%20million%20in%201935!%20Of%20the%2016%20million%20married%20women%20at%20the%20end%20of%201938%2C%2022%25%20were%20childless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20the%20chosen%20race%20of%20Aryans%20simply%20did%20not%20have%20the%20numbers%20to%20create%20and%20sustain%20the%20Third%20Reich%20became%20a%20matter%20of%20considerable%20concern%20for%20Hitler%2C%20Himmler%20and%20the%20SS.%20In%201936%2C%20Himmler%20sent%20out%20a%20circular%20that%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20SS%20has%20taken%20a%20first%20step%20in%20issuing%20the%20marriage%20order.%20But%20a%20marriage%20without%20many%20children%20is%20no%20more%20than%20an%20affair.%20I%20hope%20here%20too%20members%20of%20the%20SS%2C%20and%20particularly%20its%20leaders%2C%20will%20set%20a%20good%20example.%20Four%20children%20are%20the%20necessary%20minimum%20for%20a%20good%20and%20healthy%20marriage%20%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20entry%20into%20Poland%20marking%20the%20start%20of%20World%20War%20II%2C%20Himmler%20issued%20a%20circular%20on%20October%2028%2C%201939%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20war%20involves%20a%20tremendous%20letting%20of%20the%20best%20blood.%20Many%20victories%20won%20by%20the%20force%20of%20arms%20have%20been%20a%20shattering%20defeat%20for%20a%20nation%E2%80%99s%20vitality%20and%20blood.%20But%20the%20sadly%20necessary%20death%20of%20the%20best%20men%2C%20deplorable%20though%20it%20is%2C%20is%20not%20the%20worst.%20Far%20worse%20is%20the%20absence%20of%20the%20children%20who%20were%20not%20born%20of%20the%20living%20during%20the%20war%20and%20of%20the%20dead%20after%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20Rudolf%20Hess%20published%20%E2%80%98An%20Open%20Letter%20to%20an%20Unmarried%20Mother%E2%80%99%2C%20in%20which%20he%20wrote%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20wartime%2C%20which%20involves%20the%20death%20of%20many%20of%20our%20best%20men%2C%20every%20new%20life%20is%20of%20special%20importance%20to%20the%20nation.%20Hence%2C%20if%20racially%20unobjectionable%20young%20men%20going%20on%20active%20service%20leave%20behind%20children%20who%20pass%20on%20their%20blood%20to%20future%20generations%20through%20a%20girl%20of%20the%20right%20age%20and%20similar%20healthy%20heredity%20%E2%80%A6%20steps%20will%20be%20taken%20to%20preserve%20this%20valuable%20national%20wealth.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%2C%20then%2C%20a%20matter%20of%20numbers%3A%20the%20Teutons%20had%20to%20be%20in%20a%20majority%20so%20that%20any%20and%20every%20threat%20to%20the%20nation%20could%20be%20thwarted.%20The%20Third%20Reich%E2%80%99s%20future%20depended%20on%20breeding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarly%20incentives%20to%20encourage%20the%20reproduction%20of%20the%20preferred%20race%20included%3A%20every%20year%20on%20the%20birthday%20of%20Hitler%E2%80%99s%20mother%2C%20fertile%20women%20were%20awarded%20the%20Honour%20Cross%20of%20the%20German%20Mother.%20Women%20who%20had%20had%20more%20than%20four%20children%20were%20given%20a%20bronze%20medal%3B%20those%20with%20more%20than%20six%20earned%20silver%3B%20and%20those%20with%20more%20than%20eight%2C%20a%20gold%20medal.%20As%20a%20Nazi%20mouthpiece%20put%20it%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CHaving%20many%20children%20is%20the%20real%20meaning%20of%20life.%20That%20is%20why%20a%20man%20who%20has%20become%20the%20father%20of%20healthy%20children%20is%20worth%20more%20to%20us%20than%20all%20the%20deliberately%20childless%20priests%20of%20a%20whole%20millennium.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAnd%20a%20German%20woman%20who%20has%20given%20life%20to%20many%20children%20and%20has%20looked%20after%20them%20for%20a%20lifetime%20is%20to%20us%20a%20phenomenon%20more%20sacred%20than%20all%20the%20childless%20nuns%20our%20nation%20has%20ever%20produced.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHimmler%20often%20used%20the%20following%20analogy%20to%20support%20larger%20numbers%20of%20progeny%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CSupposing%20Bach%E2%80%99s%20mother%2C%20after%20her%20fifth%20or%20sixth%20or%20even%20twelfth%20child%2C%20had%20said%20that%E2%80%99ll%20do%2C%20enough%20is%20enough%2C%20the%20works%20of%20Bach%20would%20never%20have%20been%20written.%20The%20same%20applies%20to%20Richard%20Wagner.%20He%20was%20a%20sixth%20child.%20I%20tell%20you%20our%20culture%20would%20have%20been%20tremendously%20impoverished%20if%20in%20the%20old%20days%2C%20families%20had%20generally%20been%20limited%20to%20four%20or%20five%20children.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15153408%2F7440153_8d204fec93_o.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22689%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15153408%2F7440153_8d204fec93_o.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15153408%2F7440153_8d204fec93_o-300x215.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668224%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22494%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENazi%20policy%20encouraged%20racially%20%E2%80%98acceptable%E2%80%99%20couples%20to%20have%20as%20many%20children%20as%20possible.%20Pictured%20here%20is%20Joseph%20Goebbels%20family.%20Photo%3A%20Dan%20Iggers%2FFlickr.%20CC%20BY-NC%20SA%202.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBreeding%20%3Cem%3Efor%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20Fuhrer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E%20camps%2C%20fifteen%20of%20them%20in%201943%2C%20were%20the%20place%2C%20in%20Nazi%20fantasy%2C%20where%20the%20Teutonic%20race%20would%20be%20nurtured%2C%20and%20who%20would%20all%20be%2C%20in%20a%20description%20by%20the%20Nazi%20Party%E2%80%99s%20official%20theorist%20Hans%20Gunther%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CTall%2C%20long%20head%2C%20narrow%20face%2C%20well-defined%20chin%2C%20narrow%20nose%20with%20very%20high%20root%2C%20soft%20fair%20(golden-blond)%20hair%2C%20receding%20light%20(blue%20or%20grey)%20eyes%2C%20pink%20white%20skin%20colour.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20magnificent%20specimens%20of%20the%20Teutonic%20race%20were%20contrasted%20with%20other%20races%2C%20what%20the%20Main%20Race%20and%20Settlement%20Office%20(RuSHA%2C%20established%20in%201931)%20in%20a%201942%20pamphlet%20titled%20%E2%80%98The%20Sub-human%E2%80%99%20described%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20sub-human%2C%20that%20biologically%20seemingly%20complete%20similar%20creation%20of%20nature%20with%20hands%2C%20feet%20and%20a%20kind%20of%20brain%2C%20with%20eyes%20and%20a%20mouth%2C%20is%20nevertheless%20a%20completely%20different%2C%20dreadful%20creature.%20He%20is%20only%20a%20rough%20copy%20of%20a%20human%20being%2C%20with%20human-%20like%20facial%20traits%20but%20nonetheless%20morally%20and%20mentally%20lower%20than%20any%20animal.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWithin%20this%20creature%20there%20is%20a%20fearful%20chaos%20of%20wild%2C%20uninhibited%20passions%2C%20nameless%20destructiveness%2C%20the%20most%20primitive%20desires%2C%20the%20nakedest%20vulgarity.%20Sub-human%2C%20otherwise%20nothing.%20For%20all%20that%20bear%20a%20human%20face%20are%20not%20equal.%20Woe%20to%20him%20who%20forgets%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20early%20as%201935%2C%20the%20Nazi%20youth%20movement%20proposed%20%E2%80%98biological%20marriages%E2%80%99%20to%20give%20respectability%20to%20extramarital%20sexual%20relations%20between%20young%20people%20who%20shared%20the%20Nazi%20vision.%20Nazi%20youth%20camps%20indoctrinated%20the%20boys%20and%20girls%2C%20particularly%20the%20latter%2C%20of%20their%20duty%20to%20reproduce.%20As%20Marc%20Hillel%20and%20Clarissa%20Henry%20in%20%3Cem%3EChildren%20of%20the%20SS%3C%2Fem%3E%20put%20it%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CNazi%20character%20training%20and%20the%20sexual%20education%20that%20went%20with%20it%20thus%20largely%20took%20place%20at%20the%20camps%2C%20outings%20and%20sporting%2C%20and%20quasi-military%20meetings%20to%20which%20the%20regime%20attached%20so%20much%20importance.%20Children%20no%20longer%20belonged%20to%20their%20parents%2C%20but%20to%20the%20Nazi%20movement.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20the%20Nazi%20Party%20published%20in%20January%201921%20a%20statement%20in%20which%20they%20undertook%20to%20exclude%20women%20permanently%20from%20important%20posts%20in%20political%20life.%20Their%20role%20in%20national%20politics%20and%20life%20was%20made%20clear%3A%20the%20kitchen%2C%20the%20church%2C%20children.%20Joseph%20Goebbels%20stated%20it%20simply%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CA%20woman%E2%80%99s%20duty%20is%20to%20be%20attractive%20and%20bear%20children.%20The%20idea%20is%20not%20as%20vulgar%20and%20old-fashioned%20as%20it%20might%20seem.%20A%20female%20bird%20makes%20itself%20beautiful%20for%20its%20mate%20and%20hatches%20out%20her%20eggs%20for%20him.%20The%20removal%20of%20women%20from%20public%20life%20%E2%80%A6%20is%20only%20to%20restore%20their%20female%20dignity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Genders%20of%20Atrocity%3A%20Before%20Lynndie%20England%20There%20Was%20Ilse%20Koch%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgender%2Fgenders-of-atrocity-before-lynndie-england-there-was-ilse-koch%5C%22%3EGenders%20of%20Atrocity%3A%20Before%20Lynndie%20England%20There%20Was%20Ilse%20Koch%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20dignity%20must%20not%20deter%20the%20women%20from%20actively%20increasing%20the%20numbers%20for%20the%20Third%20Reich.%20Himmler%E2%80%99s%20order%20%E2%80%98for%20the%20whole%20SS%20police%20forces%E2%80%99%20of%20October%2028%2C%201939%20appears%20in%20an%20English%20translation%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.co.in%2Fbooks%2Fedition%2FThe_Tragedy_of_Children_Under_Nazi_Rule%2F7F1KAAAAIAAJ%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%3EKiryl%20Sosnowski%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Tragedy%20of%20Children%20Under%20Nazi%20Rule%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(1962)%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CNotwithstanding%20the%20limits%20of%20the%20perhaps%20once%20necessary%20bourgeoise%20laws%20and%20customs%2C%20it%20would%20be%20a%20great%20task%20for%20German%20women%20and%20girls%20of%20good%20blood%2C%20also%20outside%20matrimony%2C%20to%20become%2C%20not%20out%20of%20levity%20but%20out%20of%20a%20feeling%20of%20responsibility%2C%20the%20deepest%20and%20earnest%20moral%20conviction%2C%20the%20mothers%20of%20children%20begotten%20by%20soldiers%20going%20to%20the%20front%2C%20about%20whom%20only%20fate%20knows%20whether%20they%20will%20return%20home%20or%20fall%20for%20Germany.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGirls%20from%20as%20early%20as%201935%20were%20cultured%20into%20the%20belief%20that%20they%20needed%20to%20reproduce%20%3Cem%3Efor%20the%20Fuhrer%20and%20the%20Fatherland%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Reproduction%20was%20a%20moral%20and%20national%20duty%2C%20as%20one%20circular%2C%20obviously%20directed%20at%20German%20girls%2C%20of%20the%20youth%20movement%20described%20it%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20shall%20all%20today%20or%20tomorrow%20be%20able%20to%20abandon%20ourselves%20to%20the%20rich%20emotional%20experience%20of%20procreating%20in%20the%20company%20of%20a%20healthy%20young%20man%2C%20without%20troubling%20about%20the%20impediments%20that%20encumber%20the%20antiquated%20institution%20of%20marriage.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20breeding%20and%20kidnapping%20for%20the%20Fuhrer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERuSHA%20approval%20was%20required%20for%20SS%20personnel%20to%20marry%2C%20and%20the%20approval%20was%20contingent%20upon%20the%20man%20and%20woman%20proving%20their%20racial%20purity%20and%20suitability%20for%20breeding.%20In%201935%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E%20project%20was%20formally%20launched%20under%20RuSHA.%20The%20order%20launching%20the%20organisation%20stated%20as%20its%20objectives%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E1.%20To%20support%20racially%20and%20genetically%20valuable%20large%20families.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E2.%20To%20accommodate%20and%20look%20after%20racially%20and%20genetically%20valuable%20expectant%20mothers%20who%2C%20after%20careful%20investigation%20of%20their%20families%20and%20those%20of%20the%20fathers%20of%20their%20children%20by%20RuSHA%2C%20can%20be%20expected%20to%20give%20birth%20to%20equally%20valuable%20children.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn3.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3ETo%20look%20after%20those%20children.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn4.%20To%20look%20after%20the%20mothers%20of%20those%20children.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0The%201939%20orders%20from%20Himmler%20outlined%20the%20plan%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E1.%20All%20children%20of%20good%20blood%2C%20whether%20born%20in%20or%20out%20of%20marriage%2C%20whose%20fathers%20have%20died%20in%20the%20war%2C%20will%20be%20taken%20into%20guardianship%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20Reichsfuhrer-SS%20by%20special%20officers%2C%20appointed%20by%20me%20personally.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20will%20contact%20these%20mothers%20and%20will%20take%20over%20care%20for%20the%20material%20and%20spiritual%20welfare%20of%20their%20children%20until%20their%20maturity%2C%20so%20that%20no%20mother%20or%20widow%20could%20find%20herself%20in%20distress%20or%20need.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E2.%20The%20Schutzstaffel%20%5BSS%5D%20will%20take%20care%2C%20in%20case%20of%20want%20and%20distress%2C%20of%20all%20children%20born%20during%20the%20war%2C%20whether%20in%20or%20out%20of%20marriage%2C%20and%20of%20the%20mothers%20to%20be.%20When%20the%20fathers%20return%20after%20the%20war%2C%20the%20Schutzstaffel%20will%20secure%20for%20them%20additional%20economic%20aid%20on%20an%20extensive%20scale%2C%20on%20individual%20or%20substantiated%20application.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E3.%20SS-men%20and%20you%2C%20mothers%20of%20the%20children%20awaited%20by%20Germany%2C%20show%20that%20because%20or%20your%20faith%20in%20the%20Fuhrer%20and%20because%20of%20your%20desire%20for%20the%20eternal%20life%20of%20our%20blood%20and%20of%20our%20nation%2C%20you%20are%20willing%20to%20give%20new%20life%20for%20Germany%20in%20the%20same%20way%20as%20you%20know%20how%20to%20bravely%20fight%20and%20die%20for%20Germany.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20to%20be%20absolute%20confidentiality%20over%20the%20identities%20of%20the%20biological%20mother%20%E2%80%93%20photographing%20mothers%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20forbidden%20for%20this%20reason%20%E2%80%93%20and%20foster%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20June%201939%20circular%20stated%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20possible%20to%20maintain%20secrecy%20about%20the%20origin%20of%20illegitimate%20children%20born%20in%20%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E%20homes%20for%20an%20unlimited%20period.%20The%20Reich%20office%20will%20provide%20a%20certificate%20confirming%20the%20child%E2%80%99s%20Aryan%20descent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15154019%2FKidnapping-1024x666.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15154019%2FKidnapping-1024x666.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15154019%2FKidnapping-300x195.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15154019%2FKidnapping.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668225%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22546%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EKidnapping%20of%20Polish%20children%20during%20a%20Nazi-German%20resettlement%20operation.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons.%20Public%20domain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%2C%20of%20course%2C%20much%20rumour-mongering%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E%20camps%20served%20as%20brothels%20and%20stud%20farms%20for%20SS%20officers.%20Indeed%2C%20Peter%20Neumann%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.co.in%2Fbooks%2Fedition%2FThe_Black_March%2FWy0DAAAAMAAJ%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Black%20March%3A%20The%20Personal%20Story%20of%20an%20SS%20Man%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0narrates%20an%20incident%20where%2C%20having%20been%20identified%20as%20%E2%80%98of%20pure%20Aryan%20stock%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20doctor%20tells%20him%20of%20future%20plans%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYou%E2%80%99ve%20heard%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20sure%2C%20of%20the%20Lebensborn.%20You%20have%20been%20selected%20with%20five%20of%20your%20comrades%20to%20go%20to%20Westphalia.%20Our%20Fuhrer%2C%20having%20been%20advised%20by%20Rosenberg%20and%20Darre%2C%20started%20these%20establishments%2C%20in%20which%20is%20being%20produced%20for%20Germany%20that%20pure%2C%20regenerative%20blood%20which%20we%20need%20so%20badly%20for%20the%20future.%20We%20require%20young%20men%20like%20yourself%2C%20healthy%2C%20intelligent%2C%20tried-and-tested%20Nazis.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20reaches%20one%20such%20camp%2C%20he%20asks%20a%20young%20woman%20about%20the%20place.%20Coquettishly%2C%20she%20responds%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%98But%20you%E2%80%99re%20dying%20to%20know%20how%20we%20all%20go%20to%20bed%20together%20according%20to%20National%20Socialist%20regulations%3F%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%A6%20A%20strange%20thing%20for%20one%E2%80%99s%20country%20to%20ask%20of%20one.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20later%2C%20she%20says%2C%20in%20Neumann%E2%80%99s%20reportage%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%98Your%20baby-making%20machine%20is%20at%20your%20disposal%E2%80%99.%20Her%20laugh%20sounded%20false.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20you%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20pretty%20horrible%2C%20this%20business%20of%20selling%20one%E2%80%99s%20body%20as%20an%20instrument%20of%20procreation%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20later%20Neumann%20leaves%2C%20and%20thus%20ends%20what%20he%20calls%20%E2%80%9Cour%20artificial%20love%20affair%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20despite%20the%20incentives%20and%20facilities%20(such%20as%20the%20camps%20Neumann%20experienced)%20and%20threats%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E%20programme%20for%20the%20SS%20and%20Nazi%20officials%20did%20not%20produce%20the%20expected%20results.%20As%20Larry%20Thompson%E2%80%99s%201971%20essay%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cambridge.org%2Fcore%2Fjournals%2Fcentral-european-history%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Flebensborn-and-the-eugenics-policy-of-the-reichsfuhrerss%2F45858920D4BF64CAD2DC33A5D8DB8655%5C%22%3ELebensborn%20and%20the%20Eugenics%20Policy%20of%20the%20Reichsfu%CC%88hrer-SS%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20notes%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20SS%20as%20a%20whole%20failed%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20exhortations%20of%20Himmler%20and%20other%20ideologues%20to%20produce%20more%20children.%20In%20fact%2C%2061%25%20of%20SS%20were%20bachelors%20in%201939%2C%20while%20the%20married%20contingent%20%E2%80%93%20some%2093%2C%20000%20men%20%E2%80%93%20could%20muster%20little%20more%20than%20100%2C000%20children%2C%20or%201.1%20children%20per%20family%20%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%201943%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20the%20numbers%20of%20the%20future%20rulers%20of%20Europe%2Fthe%20world%20would%20not%20be%20adequate.%20Campaigns%2C%20therefore%2C%20began%20to%20capture%20the%20illegitimate%20offspring%20of%20German%20fathers%20in%20occupied%20territories%20in%20eastern%20and%20southeastern%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20Himmler%20authorised%20securing%20the%20children%20of%20%E2%80%98racially%20valuable%E2%80%99%20parents%20across%20the%20occupied%20areas.%20They%20would%20be%20placed%2C%20if%20they%20were%20deemed%20to%20be%20suitably%20Aryan%2C%20in%20German%20foster%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHimmler%2C%20always%20a%20person%20who%20could%20draft%20a%20note%20well%2C%20issued%20an%20order%20to%20make%20this%20grand%20Germanisation%20process%20official%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20all%20cases%20when%20foreign%20women%20bear%20children%20of%20German%20men%2C%20the%20same%20should%20happen%20as%20in%20the%20East.%20Mothers%20and%20children%20should%20be%20registered%20by%20us%20and%20brought%20to%20Germany%20or%20made%20to%20stay%20there%20in%20all%20cases%20when%20they%20are%20considered%20racially%20valuable.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20such%20a%20case%20I%20also%20recommend%20the%20establishing%20of%20a%20children%E2%80%99s%20home%20for%20children%20of%20foreign%20women%20and%20German%20fathers%2C%20who%20should%20be%20brought%20up%20as%20Germans.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElsewhere%2C%20he%20popularised%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98racially%20valuable%20children%E2%80%99%2C%20exhorting%20the%20SS%20and%20others%20to%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CMake%20an%20effort%20to%20exclude%20the%20racially%20valuable%20children%20from%20the%20transfer%20and%20to%20send%20them%20to%20the%20old%20Reich%20for%20them%20to%20be%20brought%20up%20in%20special%20educational%20establishments%20%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20children%20will%20receive%20German%20names%2C%20the%20root%20of%20which%20should%20also%20be%20purely%20German.%20Proof%20of%20their%20origin%20will%20be%20established%20by%20a%20special%20office.%20All%20racially%20valuable%20children%2C%20whose%20parents%20have%20died%20during%20the%20war%20or%20later%20are%20to%20be%20sent%20to%20German%20orphanages%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20children%20brought%20into%20German%20homes%20from%20Poland%20and%20other%20conquered%20territories%20were%20%E2%80%98Germanised%E2%80%99.%20This%20involved%20a%20ceremony%2C%20described%20by%20one%20%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E%20staff%20member%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20always%20a%20naming%20ceremony%2C%20and%20an%20official%20from%20the%20register%20office%20was%20always%20there%2C%20and%20the%20mothers%20put%20on%20their%20best%20clothes%20and%20smartened%20up%20the%20children%2C%20and%20the%20living-room%20%E2%80%93%20the%20day%20room%20%E2%80%93%20was%20decorated%20with%20flowers%2C%20and%20it%20was%20all%20very%20solemn%20%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EOne%20by%20one%20each%20baby%20was%20given%20its%20name%20%E2%80%A6%20and%20it%20was%20always%20a%20very%20enjoyable%20afternoon%2C%20with%20coffee%20and%20cakes%2C%20and%20it%20was%20really%20very%20nice%20indeed%2C%20with%20the%20gramophone%20records%2C%20and%20so%20on%2C%20it%20was%20always%20most%20enjoyable.%20Yes%2C%20if%20you%20want%20to%20call%20it%20that%20%E2%80%A6%20it%20was%20an%20SS%20ceremony.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15151825%2FLebensborn-christening-ceremony.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22797%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15151825%2FLebensborn-christening-ceremony.jpg%20797w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15151825%2FLebensborn-christening-ceremony-300x182.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668218%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22484%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EOne%20such%20naming%20ceremony%20at%20a%20%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20western%20Germany.%20Photo%3A%20Bundesarchiv%2C%20Bild%20146-1969-062A-58%2FWikimedia%20Commons.%20CC-BY-SA%203.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChildren%20were%20the%20property%2C%20then%2C%20of%20the%20state.%20Sex%20was%20for%20procreation%2C%20geared%20towards%20increasing%20the%20numerical%20superiority%20of%20the%20Aryans.%20Kidnapping%2C%20re-culturation%20and%20reproductive%20totalitarianism%20were%20all%20grist%20to%20the%20Nazi%20mill%20because%20they%20were%20worried%20about%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftile.loc.gov%2Fstorage-services%2Fservice%2Fll%2Fllmlp%2FNT_Indictments%2FNT_Indictments.pdf%5C%22%3ENuremberg%20indictment%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20RuSHA%20officials%20noted%20that%20among%20their%20crimes%20were%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9C%5BThe%5D%20transfer%20of%20populations%2C%20Germanisation%20of%20citizens%20of%20other%20countries%2C%20deportation%20of%20Eastern%20workers%2C%20deportation%20to%20slave%20labour%20of%20members%20of%20other%20countries%20eligible%20for%20Ger%C2%ADmanisation%2C%20kidnapping%20of%20so-called%20%E2%80%9Cracially%20valuable%E2%80%9D%20children%20for%20Germanisation%2C%20participation%20in%20the%20performance%20of%20abortions%20on%20Eastern%20workers%2C%20murder%20and%20plunder%20of%20property.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20listed%20%3Cem%3ELebensborn%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20acts%20of%20%E2%80%98kidnapping%20of%20foreign%20children%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20Germanisation%E2%80%99%20and%20describes%20how%20%E2%80%9Cnumerous%20Czech%2C%20Polish%2C%20Yugoslav%20and%20Norwegian%20children%20were%20taken%20from%20their%20parents%20or%20guardians%20and%20classified%20according%20to%20their%20%E2%80%98racial%20value%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExhortations%20to%20certain%20communities%20to%20breed%20because%20they%20will%20otherwise%20be%20overrun%20by%20other%20communities%20is%20a%20political%20plank%20that%20marks%20the%20beginnings%20of%20a%20%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E-like%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20emphasis%20on%20purity%20%E2%80%93%20and%20proscription%20of%20mixed%20faith%20and%20mixed%20community%20liaisons%20%E2%80%93%20is%20also%20a%20preliminary%20to%20a%20%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E.%20When%20the%20purity%20of%20nations%2C%20communities%20and%20bloodlines%20is%20invoked%2C%20we%20should%20ready%20ourselves%20for%20reproductive%20totalitarianisms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20whenever%20demon%20demographics%20are%20evoked%2C%20it%20should%20recall%20Nazi%20Germany%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Demon%20demographics%20%E2%80%93%20the%20numbers%20of%20%E2%80%98our%E2%80%99%20race%20needs%20to%20be%20higher%20in%20order%20to%20rule%20the%20nation%2Fregion%2Fworld%2C%20which%20is%20full%20of%20%E2%80%98other%E2%80%99%20subhuman%20races%20of%20different%20religious%20beliefs%2C%20language%20and%20cultural%20practices%20%E2%80%93%20drove%20the%20Nazi%20SS%20and%20its%20eugenics%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E%20sought%20to%20alter%20social%20mores%20and%20moral%20codes%20around%20sexuality%20and%20marriage%2C%20and%20constructed%20the%20woman%20as%20fit%20for%20only%20one%20purpose.%20It%20redefined%20the%20family%20and%20the%20role%20of%20the%20parents%2C%20even%20as%20it%20sought%20to%20redefine%20children%20%E2%80%93%20of%20the%20appropriate%20looks%20and%20genes%2C%20of%20course%20%E2%80%93%20as%20national%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThreatened%20by%20the%20mythic%20large%20numbers%20of%20the%20racial%20Others%2C%20%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E%20set%20out%20to%20manage%20Aryan%20populations.%20As%20an%20instantiation%20of%20a%20reproductive%20totalitarianism%20scrounging%20off%20the%20hate%20for%20the%20Others%2C%20%3Cem%3ELebensborn%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20Nazi%20Germany%E2%80%99s%20one%20shot%20at%20populating%20the%20Third%20Reich%20with%20its%20%E2%80%98own%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%20the%20thousand-year%20Reich%20of%20a%20pure-bred%20race%20never%20materialised.%C2%A0%20This%20is%20a%20history%20lesson%20that%20we%20should%20learn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fpramod-k-nayar%5C%22%3EPramod%20K.%20Nayar%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0teaches%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692099014000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15155116%2FLebensborn-III.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fdemon-demographics-nazi-germany-and-the-making-of-racialised-anxiety%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Exhortations%20to%20certain%20communities%20to%20breed%20because%20they%20will%20otherwise%20be%20overrun%20by%20other%20communities%20is%20a%20political%20plank%20that%20is%20reminiscent%20of%20a%20Nazi-era%20eugenics%20progamme%20%E2%80%93%20a%20history%20lesson%20we%20ought%20to%20learn.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fdemon-demographics-nazi-germany-and-the-making-of-racialised-anxiety%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Two%20years%20on%20from%20the%20Taliban%20seizing%20power%20in%20Afghanistan%2C%20women%20fight%20back%20against%20poverty%20and%20restrictions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692097740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F08%2F768x432%2Fskynews-afghanistan-taliban_6251489.jpg%3F20230815121334%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fafghanistan-two-years-on-from-the-taliban-seizing-power-women-fight-back-against-poverty-and-restrictions-12940535%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Women%20in%20Afghanistan%20have%20set%20up%20secret%20businesses%20to%20escape%20the%20brutal%20restrictions%20of%20the%20Taliban%2C%20who%20swept%20to%20power%20two%20years%20ago%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A53%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fafghanistan-two-years-on-from-the-taliban-seizing-power-women-fight-back-against-poverty-and-restrictions-12940535%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fafghanistan-two-years-on-from-the-taliban-seizing-power-women-fight-back-against-poverty-and-restrictions-12940535%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fafghanistan-two-years-on-from-the-taliban-seizing-power-women-fight-back-against-poverty-and-restrictions-12940535%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Review%3A%20Irfan%20Habib%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Maulana%20Azad%3A%20A%20Life%E2%80%99%20Is%20a%20Voice%20of%20Reason%20and%20Unity%20in%20Times%20of%20Hate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F28185829%2Fcollage-13.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20these%20times%20of%20spreading%20hate%2C%20it%20is%20balm%20for%20the%20soul%20to%20hear%20the%20voice%20of%20reason%2C%20for%20Maulana%20Abul%20Kalam%20Azad%E2%80%99s%20voice%20was%20the%20voice%20of%20reason%20infused%20with%20compassion.%20Moreover%2C%20as%20it%20was%20a%20voice%20that%20spoke%20only%20in%20Urdu%2C%20Arabic%20and%20Persian%2C%20S.%20Irfan%20Habib%E2%80%99s%20work%20in%20translating%20the%20evolution%20of%20thoughts%20in%20English%20to%20the%20lay%20reader%20(as%20against%20academics)%20stands%20as%20an%20outstanding%20contribution%20to%20national%20integration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20voice%20had%20a%20most%20unlikely%20origin.%20Azad%E2%80%99s%20family%20had%20migrated%20from%20India%20to%20the%20Hejaz%20in%20the%20mid-1800s%20as%20they%20foresaw%20that%20the%20India%20of%20the%20Mughals%2C%20where%20they%20had%20flourished%2C%20had%20run%20out%20of%20its%20time.%20Theocratic%20and%20conservative%2C%20the%20family%20moved%20to%20Makkah%20(Mecca).%20Moinuddin%20Ahmed%2C%20the%20future%20Maulana%20Azad%2C%20was%20born%20there%20in%201888%20and%20grew%20up%20there%20till%20the%20age%20of%2017%20when%20the%20family%20moved%20again%20to%20Calcutta%20(Kolkata).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20206px)%2085vw%2C%20206px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15153015%2Fimage-1223-206x300.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22206%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15153015%2Fimage-1223-206x300.png%20206w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15153015%2Fimage-1223.png%20373w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668222%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Maulana%20Azad%3A%20A%20Life%E2%80%99%20by%20S.%20Irfan%20Habib%20(Aleph%2C%20February%202023)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20education%20was%20traditional%20and%20imbued%20with%20religious%20dogma%2C%20initially%20under%20his%20father%2C%20a%20renowned%20scholar%20of%20divinity%2C%20and%20then%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20maulanas%20and%20maulvis%20after%20the%20family%20returned%20to%20India.%20He%20was%20to%20write%20later%20in%20%3Cem%3EGhubar-i-khatir%20(The%20Dust%20of%20Memories)%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20collection%20of%20letters%20and%20essays%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20my%20childhood%20was%20spent%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20people%20who%20were%20tradition-bound%20(%3Cem%3Eqadamatparast%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20where%20there%20was%20not%20even%20the%20slightest%20opening%20for%20any%20outside%20influence%E2%80%9D%20(pp.185-186).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDisgusted%E2%80%9D%2C%20says%20the%20author%2C%20by%20the%20blind%20adoration%20given%20to%20his%20father%20by%20his%20Sufi%20%3Cem%3Emurid%3C%2Fem%3Es%20(followers)%2C%20the%20young%20Mohiuddin%20turned%20to%20the%20more%20progressive%2C%20scientific%20rationalism%20of%20Sir%20Syed%20Ahmed%20Khan%2C%20which%2C%20however%2C%20remained%20Islam-oriented%20and%20Muslim-centric%20and%20led%20to%20his%20drifting%20away%20from%20the%20Aligarh%20path%20which%20he%20later%20excoriated.%20To%20this%20was%20added%20a%20fervent%20anti-colonial%20passion%20engendered%20by%20Azad%E2%80%99s%20wide%20travels%20as%20a%20young%20man%20in%20West%20Asia%2C%20then%20steeped%20in%20Wahhabism%20but%20shaken%20by%20the%20radical%20thinking%20of%20Jamaluddin%20Afghani%2C%20Rashid%20Rida%2C%20Mohammad%20Abduh%20and%20other%20reformers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20instinctive%20reaction%20was%20to%20explore%20the%20path%20to%20%E2%80%9Cunbelief%E2%80%9D.%20He%20then%20thought%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20what%20was%20always%20believed%20to%20be%20religion%20was%20merely%20a%20picture%20of%20our%20superstitions%20and%20misapprehensions%2C%20not%20religion%E2%80%9D%20(p.77).%20When%2C%20after%20much%20cogitation%2C%20he%20returned%20to%20Islam%20he%20concluded%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20practice%20of%20love%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20distinction%20of%20caste%2C%20creed%20or%20nationality%E2%80%9D%20constitute%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20basic%20teachings%20of%20the%20Quran%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(%3Cem%3ETarjuman%20al-Quran%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20first%20volume%20of%20a%20trilogy%20of%20religious%20commentary%2C%20initially%20written%20in%201915%2C%20destroyed%20by%20the%20colonial%20authority%2C%20rewritten%20several%20times%20over%2C%20polished%20and%20revised%2C%20and%20eventually%20published%20only%20some%2015%20years%20later.%20An%20updated%20version%20came%20after%20his%20release%20from%20Ahmednagar%20Fort%20in%201945).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20exploration%20of%20different%20interpretations%20of%20basic%20Islamic%20texts%20in%20the%20light%20of%20rationalism%20(%3Cem%3Eijtihad%3C%2Fem%3E)%20became%20gradually%20but%20definitively%20the%20drumbeat%20of%20Azad%E2%80%99s%20thinking.%20His%20impassioned%20anti-colonialism%20led%20to%20his%20starting%20and%20editing%20two%20periodic%20journals%2C%20%3Cem%3EAl-Hilal%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EAl-Balagh%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20sounded%20the%20call%20to%20break%20the%20fetters%20of%20British%20colonialism%20and%2C%20because%20of%20their%20widespread%20resonance%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20led%20to%20their%20being%20forcibly%20closed%20and%20the%20editor%20being%20sent%20into%20exile%20to%20a%20small%20tribal%20village%20near%20Ranchi.%20It%20was%20the%20first%20of%20a%20series%20of%20imprisonments%20that%20totalled%20nearly%20eight%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20earliest%20works%2C%20%3Cem%3ETazkirah%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Reminiscences)%20and%20%3Cem%3EKahani%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Story)%2C%20contained%20reflections%20on%20his%20family%20and%20his%20upbringing%20and%20were%20complemented%20by%20stray%20epistolatory%20references%20in%20his%20%3Cem%3EGhubar-i-Khatir%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Referring%20to%20these%20and%20others%E2%80%99%20memoirs%2C%20Azad%20remarks%20that%20much%20autobiographical%20writing%20is%20%E2%80%9Cegotistical%E2%80%9D.%20He%20appears%20to%20think%2C%20according%20to%20the%20author%20%2C%20that%20%E2%80%9Cmost%20of%20our%20self-effacing%20behaviour%20is%20actually%20a%20manifestation%20of%20our%20egoism.%E2%80%9D%20The%20world%2C%20writes%20Azad%2C%20%E2%80%9Cdoes%20not%20get%20time%20to%20measure%20their%20ego%20and%20is%20overwhelmed%20by%20its%20frank%20and%20informal%20appearance.%E2%80%9D%20(p.187)%20As%20the%20writer%20of%20my%20recent%20memoirs%20that%20have%20been%20described%20as%20unusually%20%E2%80%9Cfrank%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Chonest%E2%80%9D%2C%20I%20stand%20humbled!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fmaulana-azad-always-stressed-on-humanity-its-a-lesson-we-need-now-more-than-ever%5C%22%3EMaulana%20Azad%20Always%20Stressed%20on%20Humanity.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20Lesson%20We%20Need%20Now%20More%20Than%20Ever.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHabib%2C%20therefore%2C%20focusses%20on%20Azad%E2%80%99s%20intellectual%20evolution%2C%20ranging%20from%20Islamic%20civilisation%20to%20Islamic%20learning%2C%20and%20covering%20different%20schools%20of%20Islamic%20thought%2C%20Islamic%20mysticism%20and%20Islamic%20science%2C%20climaxing%20in%20Islamic%20nationalism.%20He%20was%20bewitched%20by%20the%20Mu%E2%80%99tazila%20school%20of%20philosophy%20that%20%E2%80%9Csought%20a%20reconciliation%20of%20faith%20with%20reason.%20This%20synthesis%20of%C2%A0%20Muslim%20theology%20with%20Greek%20logic%20gave%20birth%20to%20a%20theological%20science%20called%20ilm-i-Kalam%E2%80%9D.(p.74)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAzad%20also%20echoed%20the%20radical%20Jamaluddin%20Afghani%2C%20who%2C%20on%20a%20visit%20to%20India%2C%20declared%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Muslims%20in%20India%20have%20applied%20the%20desire%20to%20defend%20religion%2C%20or%20religious%20zeal%2C%20in%20a%20very%20bad%20way%E2%80%A6They%20believe%20they%20must%2C%20out%20of%20religious%20zeal%2C%20hate%20and%20abominate%20what%20was%20connected%20with%20opponent%E2%80%99s%20faith%2C%20even%20though%20these%20things%20were%20sciences%20and%20arts%E2%80%9D.%20(pp.%2084-85).%20Afghani%20further%20argued%20that%20there%20was%20no%20need%20to%20reinterpret%20Islam%2C%20as%20Sir%20Syed%20had%20done%2C%20%E2%80%9Cto%20make%20it%20(Islam)%20compatible%20with%20the%20requirements%20of%20modern%20science%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfghani%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cmission%20was%20to%20awaken%20Muslims%20from%20obscurantism%20and%20encourage%20them%20to%20embrace%20Western%20science%20and%20rationalism%2C%20%3Cem%3Ewhich%20he%20considered%20inherent%20in%20the%20Quran%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(p.80%2C%20italics%20added).%20So%20too%2C%20Azad%20%E2%80%9Cfound%20it%20fallacious%20to%20say%20that%20Islam%20and%20modern%20science%20are%20contradictory%E2%80%9D%20and%20blamed%20the%20ulema%2C%20declaring%20them%20%E2%80%9Ca%20hopeless%20lot%E2%80%A6We%20have%20no%20alternative%20but%20to%20ignore%20rigid%20thinking%20altogether%2C%20focusing%20on%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20new%20mind%E2%80%9D%20(p.%2081)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contradistinction%20to%20those%20of%20his%20fellow%20Indian%20Muslims%20who%20were%20concerned%20over%20the%20prospect%20of%20the%20Muslims%20becoming%C2%A0%20an%20oppressed%20minority%20in%20the%20very%20land%20they%20had%20once%20ruled%2C%20Azad%20held%2C%20%E2%80%9CHindus%20and%20Muslims%20must%20unite%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20they%20form%20one%20%E2%80%9CQaum%E2%80%99%20and%20one%20nation%E2%80%A6the%20Prophet%20said%20that%20he%20extended%20the%20hands%20of%20friendship%20to%20all%20those%20who%20lived%20in%20the%20vicinity%20of%20Medina%20and%20declared%20that%20we%20should%20be%20%E2%80%98Umma%20Vahidah%E2%80%99%2C%20one%20people.%E2%80%9D%20(p.166%20and%20136).%20He%20returned%20to%20the%20theme%20again%20and%20again%2C%20indeed%20it%20became%20the%20leitmotif%20of%20his%20thought%20process.%20Drawing%20attention%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Ccomposite%20culture%E2%80%9D%2C%20that%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHindus%20and%20Muslims%20(have)%20been%20shaping%20for%20the%20last%20one%20thousand%20years%20and%20more%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20stressed%20that%20the%20Muslims%20have%20been%20%E2%80%9Cproud%20and%20active%20partners%E2%80%9D%20in%20forging%20a%20%E2%80%9Csyncretic%20culture%20which%20occupies%20a%20distinctly%20distinguished%20place%E2%80%9D.%20(p.166)%20This%2C%20he%20concluded%2C%20had%20given%20rise%20to%20the%20two%20communities%20sharing%20%E2%80%9Ca%20common%20nationality%E2%80%9D%20(p.160).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20while%20%E2%80%9Cas%20a%20Muslim%2C%20I%20have%20a%20special%20identity%E2%80%A6I%20am%20equally%20proud%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20I%20am%20an%20Indian%2C%20an%20essential%20part%20of%20the%20indivisible%20unity%20of%20Indian%20nationhood%E2%80%9D%20(p.160).%20He%20also%20punctured%20(p.%20156)%20the%20argument%20for%20Muslim%20separatism%2C%20holding%20incontrovertibly%20that%20as%20%E2%80%9CMuslims%20number%20between%20eight%20and%20nine%20crores%E2%80%9D%2C%20(how)%20%E2%80%9Ccan%20such%20a%20vast%20mass%20of%20humanity%20have%20any%20legitimate%20reason%20for%20apprehension%20that%20in%20a%20free%20and%20independent%20India%20it%20may%20not%20be%20possible%20to%20protect%20its%20rights%20and%20interests%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Finterview-irfan-habib-ajoy%5C%22%3EInterview%3A%20Irfan%20Habib%20Debunks%20RSS%E2%80%99s%20Nationalism%20and%20Their%20Attempts%20to%20Rewrite%20History%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20implied%20that%20if%20the%20community%20divided%20into%20three%2C%20as%20it%20has%20done%20in%20the%20Partition%20of%20India%20in%201947%20and%20the%20Partition%20of%20Pakistan%20in%201971%2C%20Muslim%20vulnerability%20in%20the%20subcontinent%20would%20only%20increase.%20Hence%20his%20clarion%20call%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20need%20of%20the%20hour%20is%20a%20single%20and%20united%20nationhood%E2%80%9D.%20Jinnah%20fiercely%20disagreed%2C%20which%20is%20why%20Pakistani%20nationhood%20not%20only%20fragmented%20but%20remained%20fractured%2C%20and%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20India%20the%20future%20of%20the%20community%20is%20fragile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAzad%20mourned.%20From%20the%20steps%20of%20the%20Jama%20Masjid%2C%20he%20spoke%20to%20his%20community%20in%20October%201947%2C%20within%20weeks%20of%20Partition%20(p.266)%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20when%20I%20see%20your%20ashen%20faces%20and%20desolation%20in%20your%20hearts%2C%20my%20mind%20goes%20back%20to%20the%20past.%20%E2%80%A6I%20had%20warned%20you%20how%20the%20forces%20of%20poison%20unleashed%20by%20sinister%20designs%20would%20lead%20to%20the%20tragedy%20of%20Partition%2C%20but%20you%20refused%20to%20listen%20to%20me.%20You%20relied%20on%20your%20ignorance%20and%20today%20you%20feel%20as%20though%20you%20are%20threatened%20by%20new%20dangers%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20indeed%20they%20are%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692097256000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F28185829%2Fcollage-13.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Freview-irfan-habibs-maulana-azad-a-life-is-a-voice-of-reason-and-unity-in-times-of-hate%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20exploration%20of%20different%20interpretations%20of%20basic%20Islamic%20texts%20in%20the%20light%20of%20rationalism%20became%20gradually%20but%20definitively%20the%20drumbeat%20of%20Azad%E2%80%99s%20thinking.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A133%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Freview-irfan-habibs-maulana-azad-a-life-is-a-voice-of-reason-and-unity-in-times-of-hate%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amid%20NEET%20Row%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20CM%20Stalin%20Wants%20Education%20Shifted%20from%20Concurrent%20to%20State%20List%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F05%2F06200018%2FScreenshot-2022-05-06-at-8.00.11-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3ETamil%20Nadu%20chief%20minister%20M.K.%20Stalin%20said%20moving%20education%20to%20the%20State%20List%20from%20the%20Concurrent%20List%20of%20the%20Constitution%20is%20the%20way%20forward%20to%20scrap%20the%20National%20Eligibility%20cum%20Entrance%20Test%20(NEET)%20during%20his%20Independence%20Day%20address%20in%20Chennai%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20August%2015%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fneet-could-be-scrapped-only-if-tamil-nadu-cm-mk-stalin-claims-after-2-suicide-incidents-in-the-state-11692074572770.html%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3ELivemint%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStalin%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20come%20on%20the%20back%20of%20two%20deaths%2C%20of%20a%20teen%20and%20his%20father%2C%20who%20allegedly%20died%20of%20suicide%2C%20over%20the%20weekend.%20The%20teenager%2C%20S.%20Jagadeeshwaran%20(19)%2C%20died%20by%20suicide%20on%20Saturday%2C%20August%2012%20evening%2C%20after%20he%20was%20unable%20to%20clear%20NEET.%20The%20student%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%20P.%20Selvasekar%20(48)%2C%20was%20found%20dead%20found%20in%20his%20house%20in%20Chennai%E2%80%99s%20Chrompet%20a%20day%20after.%20The%20father%20died%20allegedly%20of%20suicide%20unable%20to%20bear%20the%20loss%20of%20his%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20in%20a%20special%20message%20to%20students%20on%20Monday%2C%20August%2014%2C%20had%20urged%20them%20not%20to%20resort%20to%20extreme%20steps%20and%20vowed%20to%20ban%20NEET%2C%20which%20both%20the%20student%20community%20and%20their%20parents%20in%20the%20state%20have%20been%20demanding%20for%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20hitting%20out%20at%20governor%20R.N.%20Ravi%20who%20refused%20to%20sign%20the%20Bills%20passed%20by%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Legislative%20Assembly%20banning%20NEET%20in%20the%20state%2C%20Stalin%2C%20in%20his%20special%20message%2C%20urged%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20to%20grant%20assent%20at%20the%20earliest%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20NEET%20exemption%20Bill%2C%20which%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20the%20collective%20will%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20also%20written%20to%20Murmu%20highlighting%20that%20the%20Bill%20adopted%20was%20the%20%E2%80%9Coutcome%20of%20Legislative%20consensus%2C%20stemming%20from%20the%20collective%20will%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Ceach%20day%20of%20delay%20in%20its%20implementation%20costs%20not%20only%20valuable%20medical%20seats%20to%20deserving%20students%20but%20invaluable%20human%20lives%20to%20our%20society.%E2%80%9D%20He%20pointed%20out%20the%20Bill%20was%20pending%20though%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20had%20given%20clarifications%20to%20comments%20raised%20by%20various%20Union%20Ministries%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStalin%E2%80%99s%20government%20had%20brought%20Bills%20on%20the%20proposed%20legislation%20to%20ban%20NEET%20in%20the%20Assembly%20twice%2C%20only%20to%20see%20them%20returned%20by%20the%20governor.%20As%20the%20matter%20pertained%20to%20the%20Concurrent%20List%2C%20the%20Bill%20was%20forwarded%20to%20the%20President%20for%20her%20assent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20DMK%20government%20and%20Ravi%20have%20had%20several%20run-ins%20over%20the%20Bill.%20Ravi%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20made%20on%20Saturday%2C%20August%2012%2C%20also%20made%20the%20Stalin%20government%20angry.%20%E2%80%9CGiven%20to%20me%2C%20I%20shall%20never%20give%20it.%20Be%20sure%20about%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ravi%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692097235000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F05%2F06200018%2FScreenshot-2022-05-06-at-8.00.11-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Famid-neet-row-tamil-nadu-cm-stalin-wants-education-shifted-from-concurrent-to-state-list%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20teen%20student%20and%20his%20father%20died%20allegedly%20of%20suicide%20in%20Chennai%20recently%20after%20the%20former%20was%20unable%20to%20clear%20NEET%20exam.%20The%20deaths%20once%20again%20brought%20the%20NEET%20issue%20to%20the%20fore%20in%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Famid-neet-row-tamil-nadu-cm-stalin-wants-education-shifted-from-concurrent-to-state-list%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Independence%20Day%20Speech%20Is%20High%20on%20Lofty%20Rhetoric%20but%20Devoid%20of%20Plan%20of%20Action%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15153118%2FH20230815136672.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20times%20of%20generative%20AI%2C%20it%20is%20easy%20to%20compile%20a%20speech%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20He%20has%20now%20delivered%20ten%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Findependence-day-modi-speech-slavery-manipur%5C%22%3EIndependence%20Day%20addresses%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20clear%20pattern%20emerges.%20He%20will%20claim%20sole%20credit%20for%20every%20achievement%2C%20often%20appropriating%20inevitable%20progress%20as%20a%20major%20success%3B%20he%20will%20ignore%20facts%20and%20deftly%20disregard%20past%20promises%2C%20and%20brush%20aside%20legitimate%20concerns%20of%20the%20people.%20His%20rhetoric%20often%20has%20a%20lofty%20vision%20that%20is%20devoid%20of%20a%20plan%20of%20action.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20economic%20front%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20has%20given%20us%20a%20%E2%80%98personal%20guarantee%E2%80%99%20that%20India%20will%20become%20the%20third-largest%20economy%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years.%20Sounds%20impressive%20at%20first%20and%20hollow%20after%20we%20realise%20that%20in%202013%20itself%20a%20report%20estimated%20that%20India%20was%20going%20to%20be%20the%20third%20largest%20economy%20by%202028.%20As%20long%20as%20policymakers%20avert%20missteps%20like%20demonetisation%2C%20a%20badly%20designed%20GST%2C%20and%20unplanned%20lockdowns%2C%20we%20(relying%20on%20a%20Goldman%20Sachs%20analysis)%20can%20guarantee%20that%20we%20will%20be%20the%20second-largest%20economy%20by%202075.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20guaranteeing%20the%20inevitable%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20mentioned%20how%20before%202014%2C%20India%20was%20grouped%20among%20the%20%E2%80%98fragile%20five%E2%80%99%20economies.%20Between%202004%20and%202014%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20growth%20averaged%207.8%25.%20In%20the%20year%202013-14%2C%20our%20supposedly%20%E2%80%98fragile%E2%80%99%20economy%20was%20growing%20at%206.4%25%3B%20and%20has%20now%20averaged%205.7%25%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years.%20India%20has%20drastically%20lost%20growth%20momentum%20and%20the%20people%20are%20suffering.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstitutional%20functionaries%20may%20have%20the%20luxury%20of%20ignoring%20facts%2C%20but%20common%20people%20don%E2%80%99t.%20Therefore%2C%20when%20the%20youth%20hear%20the%20prime%20minister%20proclaim%20that%20%E2%80%98this%20country%20will%20provide%20you%20with%20unlimited%20opportunities%2C%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20worry%E2%80%99%20they%20are%20not%20assured%20but%20overcome%20with%20a%20sense%20of%20disillusionment.%20%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYouth%20unemployment%20has%20remained%20above%2022%25%20since%202014.%20The%20mismanagement%20of%20the%20economy%20has%20shrunk%20the%20job%20market%20forcing%20people%20out%20of%20the%20workforce.%20The%20government%20could%20have%20stepped%20up%20but%20it%20chose%20to%20turn%20its%20back%20and%20disregard%20the%20plight%20of%20our%20youth.%20Last%20year%2C%20the%20Minister%20of%20Personnel%20informed%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20that%20between%202014%20and%202022%2C%2022%20crore%20government%20job%20applications%20were%20received%20whereas%20only%207.2%20lakhs%20were%20provided%20employment.%20For%20every%201%2C000%20applications%2C%20only%203%20jobs%20are%20being%20created%20in%20the%20government%20sector.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20worse%20is%20the%20continuous%20drop%20in%20recruitment.%20The%20number%20of%20candidates%20appointed%20has%20dropped%2070%25%20since%202014-15.%20In%202021-22%2C%20only%2038%2C850%20candidates%20were%20recruited%20against%201.86%20crore%20applications.%20The%20references%20to%20MUDRA%20Yojana%20as%20a%20serial%20job%20creator%20are%20misplaced.%20Almost%2080%25%20of%20the%20loans%20in%202021-22%20are%20in%20the%20Shishu%20category%20where%20the%20loan%20amount%20is%20less%20than%20Rs%2050%2C000.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20youth%20have%20fewer%20opportunities%20because%20the%20marquee%20projects%20have%20not%20come%20through.%20In%20his%202014%20speech%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20called%20upon%20the%20world%20to%20%E2%80%98come%2C%20make%20in%20India%E2%80%99.%20The%20target%20was%20to%20create%2010%20crore%20jobs%20in%20the%20manufacturing%20sector%20by%202022.%20Between%202016%20and%202023%2C%2015%20lakh%20manufacturing%20jobs%20have%20been%20lost.%20However%2C%20we%20cannot%20let%20facts%20come%20in%20the%20way%20of%20a%20speech.%20Past%20promises%20must%20be%20disregarded%20wherever%20convenient.%20Therefore%2C%20we%20do%20not%20hear%20of%20doubling%20farmer%20incomes%20anymore%2C%20or%20the%20100%20SMART%20cities%2C%20or%20houses%20for%20all%2C%20or%20electricity%20in%20every%20house.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20major%20concern%20with%20generative%20AI%20is%20that%20without%20context%2C%20it%20produces%20results%20that%20may%20vary%20significantly%20from%20the%20issue%20at%20hand.%20ChatGPT%20often%20creates%20hyperlinks%20that%20do%20not%20exist.%20Similarly%2C%20while%20listening%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20speech%2C%20it%20appeared%20to%20be%20laden%20with%20hyperbole%20and%20steeped%20in%20fiction.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20common%20people%20are%20concerned%20with%20rising%20inflation%20but%20the%20prime%20minister%20brushed%20aside%20those%20issues%20with%20aplomb%2C%20claiming%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20able%20to%20control%20inflation%20successfully.%E2%80%9D%20The%20Ministry%20of%20Statistics%20released%20inflation%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fat-15-month-high-retail-inflation-in-july-jumped-to-7-44-owing-to-soaring-vegetable-prices%5C%22%3Enumbers%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20August%2014%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20they%20tell%20us%20that%20retail%20inflation%20is%20at%20a%2015-month%20high%20and%20vegetable%20prices%20have%20increased%2038%25%20month-on-month%20and%2037%25%20year-on-year.%20Persistently%20high%20fuel%20and%20LPG%20prices%20have%20been%20hurting%20common%20people%20for%20months%20now.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dissonance%20between%20claims%20from%20Red%20Fort%20and%20the%20reality%20on%20the%20ground%20is%20not%20new.%20Today%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20once%20again%20spoke%20of%20implementing%20%E2%80%98One%20Rank%2C%20One%20Pension%E2%80%99%2C%20perhaps%20forgetting%20that%20a%20day%20before%20his%202015%20Independence%20Day%20address%2C%20jawans%20protesting%20peacefully%20in%20Delhi%20were%20allegedly%20manhandled%20by%20police%20forces.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20stressed%20upon%20women-led%20development%20and%20we%20must%20hope%20things%20don%E2%80%99t%20take%20a%20turn%20for%20the%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F11%2Fveterans-medals.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%224928%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F11%2Fveterans-medals.jpg%204928w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F11%2Fveterans-medals-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F11%2Fveterans-medals-1024x682.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-15401%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223280%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EEx-servicemen%20returning%20their%20medals%20during%20their%20agitation%20for%20the%20One%20Rank%20One%20Pension%20(OROP)%20scheme%20in%202015.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%20Photo%20by%20Subhav%20Shukla%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20no%20secret%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20anxious%20to%20leave%20a%20lasting%20legacy.%20Bombastic%20statements%20without%20positive%20change%20cannot%20achieve%20that.%20For%20three%20months%20now%2C%20people%20in%20Manipur%20have%20been%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20brutal%20conflict.%20It%20is%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20duty%20to%20step%20in%20and%20work%20towards%20building%20peace.%20People%20will%20recall%20how%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20as%20prime%20minister%2C%20initiated%20dialogue%20processes%20in%20Assam%20and%20Mizoram%20which%20culminated%20in%20the%20signing%20of%20the%20Assam%20Accord%20in%201985%20and%20the%20Mizoram%20Peace%20Accord%20in%201986.%20In%20both%20Assam%20and%20Mizoram%2C%20Congress%20governments%20were%20asked%20to%20either%20step%20down%20or%20fresh%20elections%20called%20to%20legitimise%20the%20peace%20process.%20We%20need%20more%20leaders%20who%20can%20sacrifice%20power.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20yearning%20for%20a%20fresh%20vision%20that%20places%20the%20vulnerable%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20policymaking.%20The%20Congress%20government%20in%20Rajasthan%20has%20enacted%20progressive%20laws%20to%20aid%20gig%20workers%2C%20ensure%20robust%20healthcare%20for%20all%20citizens%2C%20and%20guarantee%20a%20minimum%20income%20to%20all%20its%20citizens.%20In%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20government%20has%20responded%20to%20the%20aspirations%20of%20its%20people%20and%20is%20offering%20them%20a%20caring%20government.%20In%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20the%20pro-farmer%20and%20pro-Adivasi%20policies%20have%20led%20to%20rural%20rejuvenation.%20In%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20government%20has%20embarked%20on%20a%20welfare-oriented%20plan%20of%20action%20that%20provides%20