C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20warned%20you%20against%20domestic%20tyrants.%20Your%20Independence%20is%20not%20the%20freedom%20I%20envisaged.%20You%20insisted%20that%20independence%20was%20above%20all%20about%20reclaiming%20state%20power%20from%20foreign%20tyrants.%20My%20concept%20of%20freedom%2C%20enshrined%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EGitanjali%2035%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20was%20more%20broad-based%20and%20of%20greater%20relevance%20today%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhere%20the%20mind%20is%20without%20fear%20and%20the%20head%20is%20held%20high%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EWhere%20knowledge%20is%20free%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EWhere%20the%20world%20has%20not%20been%20broken%20up%20into%20fragments%20by%20narrow%20domestic%20walls%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EWhere%20words%20come%20out%20from%20the%20depth%20of%20truth%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EWhere%20tireless%20striving%20stretches%20its%20arms%20towards%20perfection%3B%20Where%20the%20clear%20stream%20of%20reason%20has%20not%20lost%20its%20way%20into%20the%20dreary%20desert%20sand%20of%20dead%20habit%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EWhere%20the%20mind%20is%20led%20forward%20by%20thee%20into%20ever-widening%20thought%20and%20action%20Into%20that%20heaven%20of%20freedom%2C%20my%20Father%2C%20let%20my%20country%20awake.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGandhi%20might%20have%20retorted%20to%20Tagore%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9Cl%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20simply%20struggling%20to%20capture%20state%20power%2C%20even%20though%20that%20was%20an%20essential%20part%20of%20the%20freedom%20struggle.%20l%20was%20pursuing%20Ram%20Rajya%2C%20which%20was%20not%20very%20different%20from%20your%20concept%20of%20freedom.%20I%20might%20add%20it%20was%20far%20removed%20from%20the%20Hindu%20Rashtra%20of%20Savarkar%20and%20the%20Hindu%20Right%20that%20sought%20to%20exclude%20certain%20citizens%20from%20its%20ambit.%20Ram%20Rajya%2C%20like%20your%20concept%20of%20freedom%20in%20Gitanjali%2C%20is%20an%20inclusive%20and%20just%20society%20that%20is%20not%20jingoistic.%20I%20dedicated%20August%2015%2C%201947%2C%20to%20contemplation%20and%20soul%20searching%20and%20not%20to%20a%20celebration%20of%20removal%20of%20foreign%20tyranny.%20That%20was%20only%20a%20pre-condition%2C%20and%20not%20a%20sufficient%20one%2C%20for%20freedom.%20The%20freedom%20struggle%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewas%20to%20continue%20after%20Independence%2C%20but%20I%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20pursue%20it%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETo%20which%20Tagore%20might%20have%20replied%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9CHow%20could%20you%20possibly%20have%20hoped%20to%20achieve%20Ram%20Rajya%20if%2C%20after%20capturing%20state%20power%20from%20foreign%20tyrants%2C%20it%20was%20to%20be%20handed%20over%20to%20domestic%20bigoted%20men%20of%20straw%3F%20The%20kind%20of%20people%20who%20%E2%80%93%20with%20notable%20exceptions%20like%20Nehru%20%E2%80%93%20ran%20independent%20India%2C%20and%20including%20our%20present%20leadership%3F%20Now%20the%20country%20will%20need%20to%20struggle%20for%20freedom%20all%20over%20again%2C%20this%20time%20from%20domestic%20tyrants%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20response%2C%20Gandhi%20might%20have%20then%20turned%20to%20Dr.%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20and%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20and%20reminded%20Tagore%20that%20the%20onus%20lay%20on%20these%20two%20to%20carry%20forward%20their%20vision%20for%20independent%20India.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fambedkar-women-empowerment-hindu-code-bill%5C%22%3EAmbedkar%20drafted%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20institutional%20framework%20within%20which%20the%20new%20republic%20functioned%2C%20and%20Nehru%20was%20its%20first%20helmsman%20for%20over%20a%20decade%20and%20a%20half.%20As%20a%20last%20resort%20he%20had%20left%20behind%20a%20powerful%20political%20tool%20that%20could%20be%20used%20against%20petty%20domestic%20tyrants.%20Non-violent%20satyagraha%20was%20powerful%20enough%20to%20bring%20the%20mightiest%20empire%20in%20the%20world%20to%20quit%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20constitution%20I%20drafted%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ambedkar%20might%20well%20have%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fambedkar-jayanti-untouchability%5C%22%3Eset%20in%20place%20a%20sound%20framework%20for%20the%20just%20and%20inclusive%20society%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20both%20of%20you%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Nehru%20and%20I%2C%20desired.%20It%20placed%20all%20religions%20on%20the%20same%20footing%2C%20guaranteed%20fundamental%20rights%20to%20all%20citizens%2C%20with%20special%20safeguards%20set%20in%20stone%20for%20those%20socially%20ostracised%20for%20long%2C%20and%20for%20whose%20rights%20I%20personally%20championed%2C%20and%20gave%20directives%20to%20the%20state%20to%20ensure%20social%20justice.%20I%20did%20the%20best%20I%20could%20to%20balance%20power%20between%20the%20executive%2C%20parliament%20and%20the%20judiciary%20to%20keep%20domestic%20tyrants%20at%20bay%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENehru%20might%20have%20spoken%20on%20his%20own%20behalf%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20no%20doubt%20given%20a%20constitution%20that%20had%20all%20the%20features%20that%20Ambedkar%20spoke%20of%2C%20but%20what%20could%20I%20do%20if%20my%20own%20colleagues%20were%20not%20fully%20committed%20to%20the%20values%20of%20secularism%2C%20individual%20liberty%2C%20rationalism%2C%20social%20justice%20or%20even%20to%20personal%20probity%3F%20I%20had%20personally%20taken%20up%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20peasantry%20against%20oppressive%20zamindars%20during%20the%20freedom%20struggle%2C%20but%20I%20got%20little%20support%20for%20implementing%20zamindari%20abolition%20effectively%2C%20and%20also%20the%20Hindu%20Code%20Bill.%20The%20constitution%20gave%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20the%20central%20executive%20adequate%20powers%2C%20but%20I%20wished%20to%20operate%20in%20a%20democratic%20manner%20and%20not%20become%20the%20brown-skinned%20domestic%20tyrant%20that%20Tagore%20warned%20us%20about.%20I%20lament%20that%20my%20own%20daughter%2C%20who%20should%20have%20known%20better%2C%20was%20the%20first%20chief%20executive%20to%20misuse%20the%20powers%20given%20to%20the%20central%20government%20to%20undermine%20democracy.%20It%20is%20to%20her%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ecredit%20that%20she%20backtracked%20quickly%2C%20but%20she%20nevertheless%20showed%20the%20template%20that%20tyrants%20subsequently%20built%20on.%20My%20grandson%20Rajiv%2C%20despite%20carrying%20forward%20my%20vision%20of%20a%20modern%20India%2C%20did%20not%20have%20the%20moral%20courage%20to%20taken%20on%20the%20dark%20clouds%20of%20religious%20bigotry%20that%20were%20gathering%20afresh%20over%20the%20Republic.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnarendra-modi-congress-jawaharlal-nehru%5C%22%3EPride%20and%20Shame%3A%20Who%20Should%20Apologise%20for%20Running%20Down%20India%E2%80%99s%20Achievements%20Abroad%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EAfter%20hearing%20Gandhi%2C%20Ambedkar%20and%20Nehru%2C%20this%20is%20what%20Tagore%20might%20have%20concluded%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20original%20argument%20was%20that%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20with%20notable%20exceptions%20like%20Gandhi%20and%20Nehru%2C%20were%20not%20prepared%20to%20take%20up%20the%20mantle%20of%20a%20free%20India.%20I%20held%20no%20brief%20for%20the%20British%20Raj%2C%20but%20transfer%20of%20power%20was%20only%20the%20beginning%20and%20not%20the%20end%20of%20the%20freedom%20project.%20Gandhi%20and%20I%20agreed%20on%20this.%20My%20fear%20was%20that%20this%20project%20could%20be%20abandoned%20as%20soon%20as%20India%20became%20independent%20from%20foreign%20rule.%20The%20Mahatma%20would%20no%20doubt%20have%20carried%20the%20project%20forward%20if%20he%20were%20physically%20able%20to%20do%20so%2C%20but%20perhaps%20Nehru%20who%20had%20the%20desire%20as%20well%20could%20have%20secured%20freedom%20far%20better%20had%20he%20concentrated%20less%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98commanding%20heights%E2%80%99%20of%20both%20the%20physical%20and%20soft%20(educational)%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20devoted%20his%20attention%2C%20and%20more%20resources%2C%20to%20the%20cutting%20edge%20of%20society%20where%20the%20roots%20of%20freedom%20are%20nurtured.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAmbedkar%20drafted%20a%20fine%20constitution%2C%20but%20he%20was%20perhaps%20too%20focussed%20on%20social%20justice%2C%20and%20too%20little%20on%20liberty%2C%20it%20seems%20on%20account%20of%20the%20fear%20of%20the%20new%20Republic%20falling%20prey%20to%20fissiparous%20tendencies%20that%20had%20long%20characterised%20Indian%20history.%20India%20was%20still%20a%20%E2%80%98nation%20in%20making%2C%E2%80%99%20newly%20forged%20out%20of%20a%20number%20of%20ethnically%2C%20culturally%20and%20linguistically%20diverse%20states%20that%20had%20centuries%20of%20independent%20political%20histories%2C%20with%20all%20India%20empires%20being%20few%20and%20far%20in%20between%2C%20and%20relatively%20short-lived.%20In%20order%20to%20strengthen%20the%20Centre%20the%20constitution%20gave%20it%20sweeping%20powers%2C%20including%20in%20the%20appointment%20of%20key%20constitutional%20positions%20with%20all-India%20remit%20that%20were%20expected%20to%20safeguard%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20and%20keep%20its%20key%20institutions%20at%20arms%20length%20from%20the%20executive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20ultimately%20self-defeating%2C%20as%20this%20structure%20flew%20in%20the%20face%20of%20Indian%20history%20that%20was%20characterised%20by%20substantial%20regional%20autonomy%20on%20account%20of%20its%20diversity.%20Whenever%20all-Indian%20empires%20tried%20to%20centralise%2C%20like%20the%20later%20Tughlaqs%20or%20Aurangzeb%2C%20the%20empires%20quickly%20collapsed.%20The%20British%20ruled%20essentially%20through%20three%20separate%20Presidencies%20and%20not%20from%20Delhi%20or%20London%2C%20while%20over%20a%20hundred%20subordinate%20states%20had%20their%20own%20rulers%20and%20administration.%20There%20were%20inadequate%20safeguards%20to%20keep%20determined%20autocrats%20and%20demagogues%20at%20bay.%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20focus%20of%20the%20founding%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Efathers%20of%20the%20American%20constitution%2C%20that%20Ambedkar%20also%20drew%20upon%2C%20was%20on%20defending%20freedom%20from%20would%20be%20demagogues%20who%20could%20use%20the%20will%20of%20the%20people%20to%20undermine%20democracy%2C%20drawing%20on%20the%20experience%20and%20associated%20debates%20in%20ancient%20Greco-Roman%20polity%20and%20philosophy.%20American%20institutions%20consequently%20have%20so%20far%20held%20up%20well%20in%20the%20face%20of%20would%20be%20demagogues%20and%20autocrats%2C%20while%20in%20India%20they%20collapsed%20quickly.%20Since%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20new%20Republic%20were%20still%20unprepared%20or%20not%20mature%20enough%20to%20exercise%20power%2C%20democratic%20safeguards%20should%20have%20been%20all%20the%20more%20stronger.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20we%20were%20fighting%20for%20Independence%20I%20was%20filled%20with%20hope.%20If%20I%20were%20to%20rewrite%20%3Cem%3EGitanjali%2035%3C%2Fem%3E%20with%20the%20benefit%20of%20hindsight%2C%20it%20might%20read%20as%20follows%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EWhere%20the%20mind%20is%20filled%20with%20fear%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20the%20head%20is%20crestfallen%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EWhere%20knowledge%20is%20controlled%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EWhere%20the%20world%20is%20broken%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20fragmented%20by%20narrow%20domestic%20walls%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EWhere%20the%20words%20come%20out%20from%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20depths%20of%20falsehood%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EWhere%20tired%20hands%20stretch%20out%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Etheir%20arms%20with%20diminishing%20hope%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EWhere%20the%20clear%20stream%20of%20reason%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ehas%20lost%20its%20way%20in%20the%20dreary%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edesert%20sand%20of%20bigotry%20and%20dead%20habit%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EWhere%20the%20mind%20is%20led%20backwards%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Einto%20ever-diminishing%20thought%20and%20action%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20that%20Slough%20of%20Despond%20my%20Father%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eshake%20my%20country%20awake.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Falok-sheel%5C%22%3EAlok%20Sheel%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20former%20civil%20servant%20and%20writer.%3C%2Fem%3