ernment%20had%20set%20up.%20Among%20those%2C%20he%20named%20the%20All%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20(AIIMS)%20at%20Darbhanga%20%E2%80%93%20a%20district%20town%20in%20north%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Mithila%20region.%20The%20hospital%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20constructed%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fpatna-news%2Fbihar-cm-nitish-kumar-asserts-shobhan-is-ideal-site-for-aiims-accuses-centre-of-delaying-project-for-political-reasons-101692026980286.html%5C%22%3Ehas%20led%20to%20a%20flood%20of%20back%20and%20forth%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20the%20RJD%2C%20JD(U)%20and%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-bihar-central-agencies-ajit-pawar-tejashwi-nitish%5C%22%3EDespite%20Efforts%2C%20BJP%20Fails%20to%20Pull%20an%20%E2%80%98Ajit%20Pawar%E2%80%99%20in%20Bihar%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%20leaders%20have%20come%20out%20with%20all%20guns%20blazing.%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESafed%20jhooth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(white%20lies)%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20state%20health%20minister%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20pulling%20out%20the%20official%20records%20that%20testified%20that%20the%20Bihar%20government%20had%20given%20151%20acres%20of%20land%20on%20the%20Shobhan%20bypass%20in%20Darbhanga%20free%20of%20cost%20for%20the%20AIIMS%20project.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMoreover%2C%20the%20state%20cabinet%20sanctioned%20Rs%20309.29%20crore%20for%20filling%20the%20land%E2%80%9D%2C%20Tejashwi%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJD(U)%20president%20and%20MP%20Lallan%20Singh%2C%20who%20had%20attacked%20the%20prime%20minister%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20over%20his%20silence%20on%20the%20Manipur%20violence%20on%20August%2011%2C%20said%20the%20prime%20minister%20%E2%80%9Cspoke%20lies%20habitually%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Union%20health%20minister%20Mansukh%20Mandaviya%20came%20out%20in%20defence%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20land%20allotted%20by%20the%20Bihar%20government%20in%20Darbhanga%20was%20not%20appropriate.%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Sushil%20Kumar%20Modi%20too%20defended%20the%20prime%20minister%20by%20saying%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9CJD(U)%20and%20the%20RJD%2C%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20take%20credit%2C%20relegated%20the%20project%20to%20backburner%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20fact%20remains%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20had%20made%20a%20false%20claim.%20And%20despite%20Mansukh%20Mandaviya%2C%20Sushil%20Modi%20and%20a%20plethora%20of%20Bihar%20BJP%20leaders%20defending%20the%20prime%20minister%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20Modi%20stands%20exposed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EModi%20ignoring%20%E2%80%98Modi%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20writer%20recently%20travelled%20to%20the%20north%20Bihar-Uttar%20Pradesh%20borders%20to%20find%20aggressive%20RJD%20and%20JD(U)%20cadres%20on%20the%20Bihar%20side%2C%20taking%20up%20efforts%20to%20tell%20people%20about%20the%20Nitish%20Kumar%20government%E2%80%99s%20work%20in%20health%2C%20education%20and%20civic%20infrastructure%20with%20emphasis%20on%20empowering%20women%2C%20extremely%20backward%20classes%20and%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESocial%20media%20%E2%80%93%20a%20mandatory%20tool%20in%20present%20day%20politics%20%E2%80%93%20is%20something%20that%20JD(U)%20and%20RJD%20have%20been%20making%20their%20presence%20felt%20on.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFirst%2C%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20beefed%20up%20his%20and%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20social%20media%20presence%20by%20employing%20professionals.%20Besides%20the%20official%20Twitter%20handles%2C%20parody%20accounts%20counter%20the%20BJP%20IT%20cell%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98propaganda%E2%80%99.%20The%20JD(U)%2C%20initially%20lagging%20behind%20on%20the%20social%20media%20front%20has%20augmented%20the%20same.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20not%20made%20significant%20gains%20in%20Bihar%20after%20the%20setback%20last%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELike%20in%20Haryana%2C%20UP%20and%20other%20states%2C%20Modi%2C%20after%20becoming%20prime%20minister%20in%202014%20tried%20to%20build%20his%20own%20team%20of%20party%20cadres%20with%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Econfidante%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Amit%20Shah.%20The%20duo%20might%20have%20succeeded%20in%20other%20states%20but%20they%20have%20failed%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrior%20to%20the%20dawn%20of%20Modi-Shah%20era%20in%20the%20Hindutva%20party%2C%20Sushil%20was%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20face%20in%20Bihar.%20A%20product%20of%20the%20Jayaprakash%20Narayan%20led%20%E2%80%98total%20revolution%E2%80%99%20and%20groomed%20by%20Kailashpati%20Mishra%2C%20L.K.%20Advani%20and%20A.B.%20Vajpayee%2C%20Sushil%20was%20the%20architect%20of%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20in%20Bihar%20and%20a%20link%20between%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20JD(U)%20and%20the%20BJP%20at%20the%20national%20level.%20Rooted%20in%20the%20philosophy%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20and%20the%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Vidyarthi%20Parishad%20(ABVP)%2C%20Sushil%20enjoyed%20all%20acceptance%20and%20respect%20among%20the%20cadres.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Terkeshwar%20Prasad%2C%20a%20product%20of%20the%20ABVP%20and%20Renu%20Devi%2C%20of%20Durga%20Vahini%2C%20who%20replaced%20Sushil%20as%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20after%20the%202020%20polls%20had%20grown%20under%20Sushil%E2%80%99s%20patronage.%20Even%20the%20Union%20minister%2C%20Giriraj%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20of%20late%20known%20for%20his%20anti-Muslim%20rhetoric%20too%20grew%20under%20Sushil.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-alliance-narendra-modi-nervous%5C%22%3EHas%20the%20INDIA%20Alliance%20Made%20PM%20Modi%20Nervous%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20believed%20that%20the%20Modi-Shah%20duo%20tried%20to%20promote%20Giriraj%2C%20Nityanand%20Singh%2C%20Samrat%20Choudhary%20and%20others%20at%20Sushil%E2%80%99s%20expense.%20In%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20political%20circles%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20widely%20believed%20that%20Modi%20and%20Shah%20got%20Sushil%20out%20of%20Bihar%20by%20making%20him%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20to%20promote%20their%20own%20brand%20of%20party%20leaders%20who%20could%20work%20more%20aggressively%20against%20minorities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20their%20experiment%20seems%20to%20have%20failed%20in%20the%20state.%20Giriraj%2C%20Nityanand%20and%20Samrat%20Choudhary%20have%20not%20displayed%20the%20flair%20of%20local%20leaders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20one%20crosses%20the%20Mehrauna%20Bridge%20on%20the%20Gandak%20river%20and%20enters%20eastern%20UP%E2%80%99s%20Deoria%20district%2C%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20influence%20grows.%20Right%20beyond%20the%20bridge%2C%20there%20is%20a%20signpost%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Vahini.%20The%20houses%20and%20shops%20along%20the%20Mehrauna-Laar-Deoria%20road%20have%20saffron%20flags%20fluttering%20on%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20streets%20are%20full%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3Ekanwariyas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20groups%2C%20travelling%20on%20motorcycles%2C%20jeeps%20and%20tractors%20chanting%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBol%20Bam%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shriram%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99.%20There%20are%20policemen%20to%20serve%20and%20escort%20them%20respectfully.%20This%20writer%20saw%20a%20group%20of%20kanwariyas%20getting%20frenzied%20when%20they%20reached%20a%20mosque%20at%20Salempur.%20The%20policemen%20did%20little%20to%20quell%20them.%20No%20Muslims%20were%20visible.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3ENalin%20Verma%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%2C%20media%20educator%20and%20independent%20researcher%20on%20folklore.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692084607000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F16183438%2FScreenshot-2022-08-16-at-6.34.34-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-prime-minister-and-his-party-have-lost-the-plot-in-bihar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20back%20and%20forth%20over%20'AIIMS%20Darbhanga'%20has%20revealed%20some%20truths.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A36%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-prime-minister-and-his-party-have-lost-the-plot-in-bihar%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Second%20Professor%20Quits%20as%20'Democratic%20Backsliding'%20Row%20Continues%20to%20Roil%20Ashoka%20University%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15121416%2Fcollagesab-pula.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Close%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fauthor-of-paper-on-possible-manipulation-in-2019-polls-quits-ashoka-university%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresignation%20this%20week%20of%20economist%20Sabyasachi%20Das%20from%20Ashoka%20University%3C%2Fa%3E%20following%20the%20political%20controversy%20triggered%20by%20one%20of%20his%20recent%20research%20papers%2C%20a%20second%20professor%20in%20the%20economics%20department%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fpulapre-balakrishnan%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPulapre%20Balakrishnan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20put%20in%20his%20papers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Das%20was%20an%20assistant%20professor%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ashoka.edu.in%2Fprofile%2Fpulapre-balakrishnan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBalakrishnan%20is%20a%20full%20professor%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20joined%20the%20private%20university%20in%202015%20after%20working%20at%20Oxford%20University%2C%20the%20Indian%20Statistical%20Institute%2C%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Management%20in%20Kozhikode%20and%20the%20World%20Bank.%20He%20is%20the%20author%20of%20several%20well-regarded%20books%2C%20including%20most%20recently%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fculture%2Fbooks%2Fan-uneven-economic-journey-indias-economy-from-nehru-to-modi-a-brief-history-author-pulapre-balakrishnan%2Fcid%2F1902831%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20Economy%20from%20Nehru%20to%20Modi%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20published%20by%20Permanent%20Black%20in%20association%20with%20Ashoka%20University%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Balakrishnan%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20announced%20by%20Ashoka%20and%20his%20resignation%20letter%20is%20not%20public%2C%20sources%20at%20the%20university%20said%20the%20senior%20economist%20had%20decided%20to%20leave%20%E2%80%9Cin%20solidarity%E2%80%9D%20with%20Das.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20soon%20after%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20broke%20the%20story%20about%20Sabyasachi%20Das%20quitting%2C%20Ashoka%20vice-chancellor%20Somak%20Raychaudhury%20said%20the%20university%20had%20accepted%20Das%E2%80%99s%20resignation.%20Seeking%20to%20address%20concerns%20about%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20unhappiness%20with%20his%20research%20paper%20on%20the%202019%20elections%20that%20had%20angered%20the%20Bharatiya%20janata%20Party%2C%20Raychaudhury%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMembers%20of%20the%20faculty%20have%20the%20freedom%20to%20teach%20and%20carry%20out%20research%20in%20the%20areas%20they%20choose.%20The%20university%20affords%20its%20faculty%20and%20students%20the%20most%20enabling%20environment%20for%20academic%20freedom%20at%20an%20institution%20of%20higher%20education.%20This%20academic%20freedom%20also%20applied%20to%20Mr.%20Das.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Balakrishnan%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20is%20likely%20to%20fuel%20fears%20that%20Das%E2%80%99s%20exit%20was%20prompted%20by%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20handling%20of%20the%20controversy%20caused%20by%20his%20July%2025%2C%202023%20paper%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpapers.ssrn.com%2Fsol3%2Fpapers.cfm%3Fabstract_id%3D4512936%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98Democratic%20Backsliding%20in%20the%20World%E2%80%99s%20Largest%20Democracy%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20university%20publicly%20dissociated%20itself%20from%20his%20research%20in%20a%20tweet%20on%20August%201%20and%20also%20questioned%20its%20quality%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20it%20was%20not%20peer-reviewed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20it%20is%20common%20practice%20for%20academics%20in%20leading%20universities%20across%20the%20world%20to%20upload%20drafts%20of%20their%20research%20for%20comment%20and%20discussion%20prior%20to%20eventual%20publication%20in%20a%20peer-reviewed%20journal%2C%20and%20Ashoka%20was%20widely%20criticised%20by%20academics%20in%20India%20and%20abroad%20for%20distancing%20itself%20from%20Das%20in%20this%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20he%20was%20hired%20in%202015%2C%20Ashoka%20University%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ashoka.edu.in%2Fashoka-university-attracts-faculty-from-across%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eissued%20a%20press%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%20noting%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfaculty%20strength%20at%20Ashoka%20has%20more%20than%20doubled%20this%20year%20as%20the%20best%20academics%20and%20scholars%20join%20the%20University%20from%20India%20and%20across%20the%20world%E2%80%9D%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPulapre%20Balakrishnan%2C%20Professor%20of%20Economics%2C%20shares%20his%20motivation%20to%20join%20Ashoka%20and%20says%2C%20%E2%80%98Ashoka%20has%20projected%20itself%20as%20committed%20to%20providing%20a%20world-class%20education%20in%20the%20liberal%20arts%20in%20India.%20This%20attracted%20me%2C%20as%20education%20outside%20the%20natural%20sciences%20and%20engineering%20has%20not%20received%20its%20due%20here.%20But%20above%20all%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20aim%20to%20be%20world%20class%20in%20whatever%20you%20do.%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20fallout%20on%20Ashoka%2C%20news%20of%20Balakrishnan%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20will%20be%20seen%20as%20further%20evidence%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaacademicfreedom.net%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimperilled%20state%20of%20academic%20freedom%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20Ashoka%20University%20administration%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20seek%20a%20comment%20on%20Balakrishnan%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20and%20will%20update%20this%20story%20when%20we%20receive%20a%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692082486000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15121416%2Fcollagesab-pula.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fsecond-professor-quits-as-democratic-backsliding-row-continues-to-roil-ashoka-university%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20resignation%20of%20senior%20faculty%20member%20Pulapre%20Balakrishnan%20is%20likely%20to%20fuel%