re%20source%3A%20Somashekar%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20process%20involved%2C%20Somashekar%20says%20it%20begins%20in%20June%20first%20week%20before%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20monsoons.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20interact%20with%20the%20farmers%20and%20have%20meetings%20in%20the%20factory%20premises%20where%20we%20highlight%20the%20benefits%20of%20cultivating%20millets%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20a%20farmer%20agrees%2C%20we%20give%20them%20a%20company%20letter%20with%20the%20MSP%20(Minimum%20Support%20Price)%20clearly%20mentioned.%20This%20letter%20assures%20them%20that%20we%E2%80%99ll%20provide%20seeds%20for%20free%20each%20season.%20We%20consult%20with%20them%20to%20choose%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F310545%2Fmp-lahari-bai-baiga-tribal-woman-preserves-rare-millets-seed-bank-ambassador-year-of-millets%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20right%20seeds%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20season.%20After%20they%20cultivate%20the%20seeds%2C%20we%20buy%20them%20back.%20This%20eliminates%20their%20concern%20about%20finding%20a%20market%20for%20their%20seeds%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20relief%20for%20farmers%20because%20lugging%20quintals%20of%20millet%20across%20state%20lines%20to%20sell%20is%20not%20a%20wise%20option.%20He%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20farmers%20bring%20the%20millets%20to%20the%20factory%2C%20we%20give%20them%20the%20promised%20MSP.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20factory%2C%20local%20women%20from%20the%20village%20participate%20in%20the%20cleaning%20and%20segregating%20process.%20Once%20they%20deem%20the%20quality%20fit%2C%20the%20millets%20are%20processed%20into%20value-added%20products%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20millet%20%3Cem%3Edosa%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20millet%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20malt%2C%20etc.%20These%20products%20are%20sold%20through%20Am