ndemic%2C%20there%20were%20only%20a%20couple%20of%20us%20comics%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Ayushi%20Jagad%2C%20Manvendra%20Singh%2C%20Ankur%20Tangde%20and%20I%20%E2%80%94%20who%20were%20openly%20talking%20about%20our%20queer%20lives.%20Today%2C%20we%20have%20about%2020%20comics%20who%20are%20out%20and%20proud.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20done%20sold%20out%20shows%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20are%20looking%20to%20do%20the%20same%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20Kolkata%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Navin.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20that%20it%20takes%20grit%2C%20money%2C%20and%20resources%20to%20set%20up%20these%20shows.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20queer%20comics%2C%20we%20want%20to%20create%20spaces%20where%20other%20queer%20people%20can%20just%20vibe%2C%20thrive%20and%20nobody%20can%20tell%20us%20anything.%20I%20live%20for%20that.%20What%20we%20have%20done%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%20is%20try%20our%20best%20to%20make%20this%20a%20safer%20space%20for%20the%20coming%20generations.%20Today%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20venues%20are%20pro-queer%20rights%20like%20Depot%2048%20in%20Delhi.%20Another%20example%20is%20the%20Social%20chain%20of%20cafes%2C%20which%20has%20been%20so%20proactive.%20They%20host%20the%20Queer%20Comedy%20Mic%20for%20us%20too.%20These%20are%20small%20steps%2C%20but%20we%E2%80%99re%20doing%20what%20we%20can%20joyfully%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20Navin%20utilises%20his%20public%20speaking%20engagements%20to%20address%20corporate%20and%20educational%20spaces%2C%20fostering%20understanding%20and%20inclusivity%20for%20queer%20individuals%20in%20professional%20and%20academic%20environments.%20His%20impact%20extends%20far%20beyond%20the%20Indian%20comedy%20circuit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FS