en%20harassed%2C%20sexually%20molested%2C%20or%20was%20about%20to%20be%20slaughtered%20illegally.%20There%20are%20ways%20to%20fight%20against%20such%20atrocities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20years%2C%20Sai%20has%20been%20reporting%20cases%20of%20violence%20against%20animals%20to%20the%20local%20police.%20Many%20of%20them%20violate%20rules%20under%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Animal%20Preservation%20Act%2C%20IPC%20429%2C%20Prevention%20of%20Cruelty%20to%20Animals%20Act%2C%20and%20Food%20Safety%20and%20Standards%20Act%20(FSSA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20cases%20that%20are%20pending%20in%20lower%20courts%20including%20dog%20poisoning%2C%20cattle%20trafficking%20and%20animal%20abuse%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20he%20also%20started%20sensitisation%20of%20police%20officers%20towards%20animal%20cruelty.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20conducting%20seminars%20in%202021%20and%20have%20reached%20out%20to%20nearly%202%2C000%20police%20offers.%20It%20is%20important%20because%20many%20officers%20in%20rural%20areas%20were%20not%20aware%20of%20the%20laws%20against%20animal%20abuse%20and%20the%20correct%20measures%20to%20take%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESai%E2%80%99s%20inbox%20and%20phone%20are%20always%20buzzing%20with%20requests%20from%20people%20all%20around%20the%20city%20as%20well%20as%20the%20outskirts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThree%20years%20ago%2C%20we%20found%20a%20cow%20that%20had%20met%20with%20an%20accident%20and%20injured%20its%20leg.%20It%20was%20in%20deep%20pain%20and%20needed%20immediate%20attention.%20I%20had%20seen%20many%20of%20Sai%E2%80%99s%20reels%20on%20Instagram%20and%20was%20aware%20of%20his%20work.%20So%20I%20called%20for%20his%20help%2C%20and%20he%20rescued%20the%20cow%20and%20took%20it%20to%20his%20sanctuary%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kathir%20Selvan%20who%20has%20been%20in%20touch%20with%20Sai%20ever%20since.%20He%20now%20informs%20Sai%20of%20any%20ani