%20cared%20for%20well.%20For%20example%2C%20in%20case%20of%20paralysis%2C%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20defecate%20themselves.%20We%20teach%20people%20how%20to%20help%20them%20do%20that.%20For%20tick%20and%20flea%20care%2C%20you%20can%20simply%20massage%20eucalyptus%20oil%20on%20the%20skin.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMypalclub%20focuses%20on%20low-income%20areas%20in%20Thane.%20%E2%80%9CLarge%20societies%20and%20people%20with%20resources%20know%20that%20they%20can%20take%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F273674%2Fwelfare-for-animals-in-goa-started-by-real-life-hero-atul-sarin%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanimal%20to%20a%20veterinarian%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20have%20the%20resources%20for%20the%20same.%20We%20work%20in%20places%20where%20they%20don%E2%80%99t.%20In%20certain%20cases%2C%20where%20people%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20the%20medicines%2C%20we%20pay%20for%20that.%20Where%20people%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20means%2C%20we%20help%20them%20with%20pet%20food%20also.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHelping%201%2C000%20animals%20a%20month%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmypalclub-min-1691406839.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Animals%20being%20treated%20on%20field%20by%20Mypalclub%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmypalclub-min-1691406839.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmypalclub-min-1691406839-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmypalclub-min-1691406839-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmypalclub-min-1691406839-768x40