bit%20Insertion%20(LOI)%20maneuver%20was%20completed%20successfully%20today%20(August%2005%2C%202023).%20With%20this%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FChandrayaan3%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Chandrayaan3%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20successfully%20inserted%20into%20a%20Lunar%20orbit.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20next%20Lunar%20bound%20orbit%20maneuver%20is%20scheduled%20tomorrow%20(August%2006%2C%202023)%2C%20around%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FIC3MMDQMjU%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FIC3MMDQMjU%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20LVM3-M4%2FCHANDRAYAAN-3%20MISSION%20(%40chandrayaan_3)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchandrayaan_3%2Fstatus%2F1687831700452098048%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%205%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20successful%20completion%2C%20India%20will%20become%20the%20fourth%20country%20to%20achieve%20a%20lunar%20soft%20landing%20after%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20former%20Soviet%20Union%2C%20and%20China.%20Both%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20former%20Soviet%20Union%20failed%20many%20times%20before%20they%20successfully%20landed%20on%20the%20Moon.%20China%20was%20the%20only%20country%20to%20succeed%20in%20its%20first%20attempt%20with%20the%20Chang%E2%80%99e-3%20mission%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691408722000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D326455%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chandrayaan-3%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20lunar%20mission%20launched%20by%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%2C%20recently%20shared%20some%20stunning%20captures%20of%20the%20Moon.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20what%20we%20can%20expect%20next.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326455%2Fisro-chandrayaan-3-updates-first-pic